Commentary: Hint of swing straightaway! Length delivery, on off, coming back in, at 133 clicks. Latham pushes it to mid off.
Little fuller this time, on off. Tom Latham covers the line and pushes it to mid off again.
Well bowled! Good-length ball, outside off, shaping away. Tom Latham shoulders arms.

Lovely stuff! Taskin Ahmed switches to 'round the wicket and bowls a good-length ball, on middle, jagging back a long way. Tom Latham doesn't read the line and he shoulders arms. He gets hit near the box. Half an appeal for an LBW but it was going well over the stumps.
Tom Latham is underway! A shapr inswinger, on off. Tom Latham pushes at it. The ball goes off the inside half of the bat to mid-wicket for a run.

Switches back to over the wicket to the right-hander. Good-length ball, around off, nipping away. Will Young looks to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge. Good first over from Taskin Ahmed. He is getting the ball to move nicely. Just a single off it.
Good length, outside off, shaping away. Latham leaves it alone for the keeper.
Length and outside off. Latham leaves it alone yet again.
Touch fuller, outside off. It flies off the deck and nips in a bit. Latham shoulders his arms and the ball brushes off his thigh pads towards the keeper.
Outside off, left alone by Latham.
Full and on leg. Latham flicks it to the leg side.
Length and on off. Latham defends it out. A maiden to start with for Islam.
Good length, outside off, shaping away. Young leave it alone for the keeper.
Fraction full and outside off, moving away. Young shoulders his arms.
On a length, outside off, moving away. Young has no interest to play away from his body.
Ahmed firs in a yorker, in the blockhole. Young blocks it out solidly.
Fuller and on leg. Young squeezes it out to mid on.
Full length and on off. Young defends it out off the front foot.
Full and on off. Latham works it to mid on off the inner half.
Good length and outside off, no movement this time. Latham covers his stumps and shoulders his arms to it.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Liton Das takes a stunner behind the stumps to sent back the Kiwi skipper, Tom Latham. A full-length ball, around off, Latham looks to drive it to the off side but gets an inside edge on it. The ball flies to the left of the keeper. Das dives low to his left to take a sharp catch. It wouldn't have carried to the first slip fielder and Liton Das has done really well to dive full stretch to his left and grab it one-handed. Tom Latham walks back to the pavilion for a timid score. He is livid with himself. Shoriful Islam is pumped up and has provided Bangladesh with an early breakthrough. Just what they needed.
Howout: c Liton Das b Shoriful Islam

Commentary: Fuller and outside off. Conway works it to mid-wicket off the inner half.
Back of a length, outside off, left alone.
Fuller and on the stumps. Conway was thinking about leaving it but in the end he defended out watchfully. A wicket-maiden from Shoriful Islam!
BEATEN! Good bounce and carry. On a length, outside off, shaping away a bit. Young looks to defend it out but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Back of a length, outside off, shaping away. Young leaves it alone for the keeper.
Length and outside off, Young blocks it to point.
Short and outside off, Young shoulders his arms.
Good length, outside off. The ball flies off the deck. Young leaves it alone. Das collects it besides his head.
Touch short and outside off. Young leaves it alone without any hesitation.

NOT OUT! Devon Conway survives. This was really, really close but the umpire's call helps Conway to stay in the middle. A length ball, outside off, shaping in. Conway looks to defend it out but misses and gets hit on the pads. Shoriful Islam appeals but the umpire shakes his head. Shoriful Islam convinces his skipper and they take the review. It shows umpire's call on impact and ball hitting the wicket. Bangladesh do not lose a review here.
Full length and on off. Conway blocks it out.
Touch fuller, outside off. Conway watches the ball closely and makes a leave.
Length ball, on off. Devon Conway nudges it to mid on.
Good length and wide outside off, Conway shoulders his arms.

Full length and outside off. Conway looks to drive it away. The ball takes the outside edge and goes to the right of gully. The fielder there dives to his right to make a good stop. This one just fell short of the man there. Third consecutive maiden for Shoriful Islam.
Length and on off. Young defends it out solidly.
Back of a length, outside off. Young does not chase it at all.
Fuller and sliding down leg. Young looks to flick it away but misses.
Full and on leg. Young looks to defend it but misses. He gets rapped on the pads. Ahmed appeals but the umpire is unmoved. Probably sliding down leg.
Outside off, left alone.
Good length and outside off. Young shoulders his arms to it.
Full, around middle and leg. Conway flicks it towards mid-wicket.
On a length, wide outside off. Conway leaves it alone for the keeper.

CLOSE! Both the batters are yet to get off the mark. On a length, outside off, shaping in. Conway shoulders his arms and leaves it alone. The ball comes back in nicely and goes over the stumps. Good leave by Conway though.
Conway is off the mark now. Good length, on off. Conway defends it to cover and gets across to the other end.
Nicely bowled! On a length, outside off, shaping away from the right-hander. Young gets on his front foot and looks to defend it out but misses.
Full length and on off. Young defends it back to the bowler.
Length and wide outside off. Conway leaves it alone watchfully.
Full and on off. Conway presses forward and defends it to the off side.
Back of a length and outside off. Conway shoulders his arms to it.
Good length, outside off. Conway keeps his blade close to his body and lets the ball sail past him.
Short ball and outside off. Conway leaves it alone watchfully for the keeper.
Full length and on off. Conway strides forward and defends it to mid off.
FOUR! Young gets off the mark with a boundary. First boundary of the innings as well. Fuller, on middle and leg. Young comes forward and flicks it through mid-wicket for a boundary.
Length and on leg. Young tucks it to square leg for a run.
Good-length ball, outside off, Conway lets it go to the keeper.
Full length and on off. Conway defends it to point solidly.
Short and on middle. Conway pulls it through square leg for a single.
Short ball and on off. Young ducks under it and leaves it alone.
Fuller, on middle. Devon Conway works it to mid-wicket for a run.
Back of a length, on middle. Will Young stands up on his toes and blocks it out.
Good-length ball, on middle, angling in. Will Young defends it out.
Good running! On the pads, fuller. Will Young flicks it to deep square leg. He calls for two and gets it. Devon Conway races back for the third run and gets it comfortably.
Good timing on that one but will only get two! Fuller, outside off. Devon Conway drives it through covers for a couple.
On a length, on off. Devon Conway plays it towards covers.
Full and outside off. Young blocks it to mid off.
Back of a length, outside off. Young punches it to point off the back foot.
Full and on off. Blocked out.
Full and outside off. Young defends it to cover.
Outside off, left alone.
Back of a length, outside off. Young shuffles across and shoulders his arms.
Full and outside off. Conway defends it out to the off side.
Length and outside off. Conway leaves it alone for the keeper.
Short and outside off. Conway pulls it off the bottom end towards mid on. The fielder there dives to his right to make the stop.
Fuller and on off. Conway defends it out solidly.
Swing and a miss! Back of a length, outside off, shaping away. Conway stays back and looks to cut it away but misses, as the ball bounces over his blade.
Full, on leg. Conway flicks it to mid-wicket for a single.
Not far away from hitting the pads! Good-length ball, on middle, nipping in. Devon Conway nudges it to square leg. Taskin Ahmed will have to reload again as he has overstepped. No ball signalled.
On a good length, on middle. Devon Conway defends it down onto the deck.
Switches to 'round the wicket. Fuller in length, outside off. Devon Conway nicely pushes it towards covers and rotates the strike.
Length ball, on off. Will Young wrists it to deep square leg for a brace.
Back of a length, on off. Will Young hops and defends it back to the bowler.
Back of a length, on middle now. Will Young looks to tuck but gets an inside edge onto the pads.
Fuller in length, on off. Will Young prods and drives it back to the bowler.
Fuller, outside off. Devon Conway does not offer any stroke to that one.
Good-length ball, outside off. Devon Conway shoulders arms.

FOUR! Lovely shot and lovey piece of timing on that one! Length ball, outside off. Devon Conway plants his front foot and pushes it late. Hits it through covers and gets a boundary. No need to run for those.

Good comeback from the bowler! Good-length ball, around off, shaping away. Devon Conway is all squared up in his defence. The ball zips past the outside edge and carries through to the keeper. Hal-hearted appeal for caught behind but nothing from the umpire.
FOUR! Second boundary of the over. Ebadot Hossain goes short now, on off. Devon Conway hangs back and pulls it through mid-wicket for a boundary. Runs have started to flow now for New Zealand.
On a length, on off. Devon Conway knocks it back to the bowler.
On a good length, on off. Will Young dabs it through backward point and gully for a couple of runs.
Short of a length, on middle. Will Young looks to pull but the ball perhaps stays a touch low. It goes off the bottom edge to the slip cordon.
Fuller in length, on middle. Pushed back to the bowler.
On a good length,outside off. Will Young is happy to leave that one alone. This is where New Zealand have been very good. Leaving balls that are outside off stump.
FOUR! Exquisite timing! Length ball, on middle. Will Young prods and drives it past mid on. The fielder gives it a chase but the ball wins the race. A boundary.
On a length, on off. Will Young stays solid in his defence.
Good start from Shoriful Islam! Good-length ball, on off. Devon Conway looks to push. The ball goes off the inner half to square leg for a run.
On a good length, on middle. Will Young clips it to mid-wicket.
Length ball, angling away, outside off. Will Young shoulders arms.
On the pads, tucked to mid-wicket.
That's gone through gully! On a length, on middle, angling away. Will Young looks to defend. The ball goes off the outside edge past the diving gully fielder for a single.
On middle, Devon Conway defends it out.
Little bit loose from Will Young. He needs to be more disciplined. This was very full, outside off. Will Young looks to drive but fails to connect.
Short of a length, on middle. Will Young mistimes his pull back to the bowler.
Fuller, outside off. Pushed towards covers.
Good-length ball, outside off. Left alone.
Back of a length, on middle. Will Young looks to work it on the leg side but gets hit on the thigh pads.
A single to end the over! On a length, on middle. Will Young clips it to mid-wicket for one.
On a length, outside off. Will Young lets it sail through.

Short of a length, on middle. Will Young pulls it without any timing to deep backward square leg. He carries it on a bounce. The fielder was in two minds there, whether to charge ahead to collect it or not. In the end, doesn't as the ball was travelling very fast. Shoriful Islam is really disappointed there. He feels the fielder should have opted for a catch.
Full and on off. Blocked out.
Length ball, outside off. Left alone.
Devon Conway works this full ball to mid on for a single.
Back of a length, around off. Will Young evades the line and leaves it untouched.
Length ball, on middle. Devon Conway clips it through mid-wicket for a brace.
On a length, on off. Devon Conway plays it on the leg side.
Fuller in length, on middle. Devon Conway flicks it to deep mid-wicket. The fielder cuts it off and keeps it down to three runs.
On a length, outside off. Will Young leaves it alone.
Length ball, on middle. Will Young defends it watchfully.
Good-length ball, outside off. Will Young looks to punch but gets beaten on the outside edge.
FOUR! Nicely played! Fuller in length, on off. Devon Conway drives it past the diving mid on fielder and collects a boundary. Glorious on-drive that!
FOUR! Back-to-back boundaries! Full again, on middle. Devon Conway flicks it through mid-wicket for another boundary. 50-run partnership comes up between these two.
On a length, on middle. Devon Conway is solid in his defence.
On a good length, on off. Devon Conway looks to defend but the ball hits the handle of the bat.

On a length, on middle, coming back in. Devon Conway looks to defend but gets hit on the pads. The ball lobs up in the air and goes towards point. The fielder catches it and appeals for a catch but the umpire is unmoved.
Length ball, on off. Tapped towards covers for a single.
Fuller in length, on off. Devon Conway pushes it to mid off.
FOUR! Conway gets away with this one! Back of a length, outside off. Devon Conway looks to pull. The ball goes off the top edge and flies over the keeper's head for a boundary.
Pushes this one wider, outside off. Devon Conway lets it sail through.
On a length, outside off. Left alone.
Back of a length again, on middle. Devon Conway this time gets his pull shot right but hits straight to square leg. He is disappointed.
Short and wide outside off. Devon Conway offers no stroke.
Starts with a loopy ball, on middle. Will Young defends it out.
Tossed up, on middle. Will Young works it behind square on the leg side.
Full and on middle, blocked out.
Full and on off, pushed to mid on for a single.
Slower through the air, outside off. Devon Conway drives it towards covers.
Loopy ball, on middle. Pushed back to the bowler.
On a length, on off. Will Young taps it towards covers for a single.
On a length, on off. Devon Conway defends it towards covers.
Devon Conway clips this length ball to mid-wicket for a run.
FOUR! Well played! Short of a length, on middle. Will Young gets into the position early and pulls it to deep square leg for a boundary.
On a length, on middle. Pushed to mid on.
Play and a miss! Good-length ball, outside off. Will Young goes in searching for the expansive drive but misses.
Loopy ball, outside off. Devon Conway pushes it towards covers.
This is defended back to the bowler.
On the pads, tucked on the leg side.
Loopy ball, on off. Blocked out.
Full and on middle, Conway clips it to short leg.
A maiden! Tossed up on off. Devon Conway is solid in his defence.
On a length, on off. Will Young defends it back to the bowler.
Good-length ball, outside off. Left alone.
Outside off again. Will Young leaves it for the keeper to collect.
Length ball, outside off. Will Young shoulders arms.
Length ball, on top of off. Will Young covers the line and pats it back to the bowler.
Short and wide, outside off. Will Young punches it off the back foot through covers. Gets a couple of runs.
Tossed up, on middle. Devon Conway defends it out.
Outside off. Left alone.
Full and on middle. Devon Conway presses forward to block.
Loopy ball on off. Devon Conway is solid in his defence.
NO BALL! On off, blocked out. The umpire signals a no ball as Mehidy Hasan has overstepped.
Floats it up, on middle. Devon Conway blocks it out.
On middle and leg. Devon Conway stays in his crease and blocks it to the off side. THAT WILL BE LUNCH ON DAY 1!
Excellent start! Good-length ball, in the fourth stump channel, angling away. Will Young looks to defend but the ball whistles past the outside edge.
On a good length, on middle. Will Young blocks it from the crease.
Good-length ball, outside off. Will Young shoulders arms.

That's a beauty! Good take from Liton Das! Good-length ball, on middle, coming back in. Will Young prods and looks to defend. He misses and the ball jags a long way back in to miss the ouside edge. Liton Das does well to dive to his right and collect the ball. Well, well, well, the replay shows there was an inside edge but no one appealed. Will Young gets a lifeline.
Fuller, on off. Played to mid on.
Back of a length, outside off. Will Young shoulders arms.
Loopy ball, on off. Devon Conway comes forward and defends it to covers.
On off, punched to the off side.
Loopy full toss. Devon Conway whips it to mid-wicket.
This is pushed back to the bowler.
Tossed up, on middle. Devon Conway uses his feet and defends it out.
Full and outside off, driven towards long off for a single.
Sprays a length ball down leg. Devon Conway looks to flick but misses.

Sprays a length ball again, down the leg side. Devon Conway looks to flick but misses yet again. This time the ball brushes his pads and goes to the keeper. Bangladesh appeal for a caught behind but the umpire says no. They decide not to challenge the umpire.
On a good length, on off. Devon Conway looks to defend but the ball hits the shoulder of the bat.
Length ball, on middle. Devon Conway works it to mid-wicket.
Three runs! Length ball, on middle. Devon Conway works it with the angle to deep mid-wicket for three runs. Moves to 40!
Back of a length, on off. Will Young defends it back to the bowler.
Loopy ball, on off. Devon Conway pushes it to long off for a single.
Tossed up, on middle. Will Young defends it out.
Short and on middle, played to mid-wicket.
On middle and leg, tucked to square leg.
Full and on middle, Young drills it to long on for one.
Too easy and comfortable for Devon Conway! Full and outside off, driven through covers for a single.
On a good length, outside off. Devon Conway fends it to the off side.
Fullish and on off, pushed to mid on.
Length ball, outside off, swinging away. Devon Conway defends it to the off side.
Back of a length, on off. Devon Conway punches it towards covers.
Nice timing! Fuller in length, on off. Devon Conway pushes it past mid off. Mominul Haque gives it a chase and slides to keep the ball in play. Saves a run for his side.
Three again! Fuller and outside off, Will Young drives it through covers. Shadman Islam does well to slide and keep the ball inside the boundary line. The batters run three.
Tossed up, on off. Will Young covers the stumps and blocks it out.
On the pads, tucked to square leg.
Loopy ball, on off. Will Young stays solid in his defence.
Full and on off, blocked out.
Full again, on off. Will Young defends it right under his eyes.
A maiden! Loopy ball, on middle and leg. Will Young clips it to square leg.
Fuller in length, outside off. Devon Conway drives it crisply but straight to covers.

On a good length, on middle. Devon Conway looks to work it on the leg side but misses. Extra bounce on that one and he gets hit on the pads. Halg-hearted appeal for an lbw but not given. Height was the issue there.
On a length, outside off. Devon Conway leaves it alone.
Fullish and on middle, clipped to square leg.
Good shot and good fielding! Fuller in length, on off. Devon Conway pushes it to mid off. Mominul Haque dives to his left and half-stops the ball. The batters take a single.
Outside off. Will Young leaves it watchfully.

SIX! BANG! Short and on off. Conway stands tall and smokes it over the mid-wicket fence for a biggie. He also gets his FIFTY. A brilliant knock from him. Becomes the first Kiwi batsman to score 4 fifty plus scores in his first 7 Tests.
Full and outside off, driven to covers.
FOUR! Floated, full and on off. Conway drives it through point for a boundary.
On off, pushed out.
FOUR! Top shot! Full and on leg. Conway gets low and sweeps it behind square for a boundary.
Tossed up, around off. Conway defends it out watchfully.
On a good length, outside off. Will Young shoulders arms.
Good-length ball, outside off. Will Young looks for a booming drive but gets beaten on the outside edge.
That's a good line! On a good length, outside off, little bit closer to the off stump. Will Young shoulders arms.
Fuller, on off. Driven back to the bowler.
Full and outside off, driven to covers this time.
Good-length ball, around off. Will Young dabs it back to the slip cordon. A tight over from Ebadot Hossain!
Loopy ball, on off. Devon Conway blocks it out.
Full and on middle, clipped to mid-wicket.
Flatter and quicker, on off. Devon Conway stays solid in his defence.
Shortish and on off, pushed back to the bowler off the back foot.
Outside off, pushed towards covers.
Tossed up, on middle. Devon Conway defends it on the leg side. Back-to-back maiden overs for Bangladesh!
Back of a length, on off, angling in. Will Young clips it to square leg.
Length ball, on off. Will Young meets it with a dead bat.
On a good length, outside off. Will Young leaves it alone.

Full and straight, on middle. Will Young flicks it to mid-wicket. Devon Conway calls for a single but is sent back. There is a shy at the bowler's end by the mid-wicket fielder but he misses to hit the stumps. Devon Conway was well in though.
FOUR! Nice touch! Short and wide, Will Young stays low and cuts it through backward point for a boundary.
Good-length ball, on off. Will Young defends it to point.
On off, pushed to long off for a single.
Loopy ball, on off. Will Young defends it on the off side.
FOUR! Lovely shot! Tossed up, on off. Will Young gets low and sweeps it behind square on the leg side for a boundary. Brings up the 100-run partnership as well.
Loopy ball, on off. Worked to mid-wicket for a single.
Outside off, defended towards covers.
Full and outside off, driven towards covers.
Length ball, on off. Will Young looks to push. The ball goes off the inside half of the bat to mid-wicket for a single.
Length ball, outside off. Devon Conway defends it to the off side.
Fuller in length, on off. Devon Conway blocks it out. These two have been very solid so far. Have not given anything away.
Full again from 'round the wicket, outside off. Devon Conway drives it to cover.
FOUR! Put away! Conway is not going to miss out on those. This was short and wide, outside off. Devon Conway stays back and cuts it past point for a boundary.
Better reply from Taskin Ahmed! Full and on off, played to mid on.
Loopy ball, on middle. Will Young tucks it to mid-wicket.
Full and on off, clipped to square leg.
Loopy ball, on middle. Will Young punches it to long on for a single.
Outside off, pushed towards covers.
Tossed up, given some air, on off. Devon Conway presses forward to block it out.
Full and on off, defended out solidly by Conway.
Solid defence! Fuller in length, on off. Will Young defends it out.
Good-length ball, outside off. Will Young lets it sail through.
Touch fuller, outside off, nipping in. Will Young leaves it alone for the keeper to collect.
FOUR! Shot of class! Fuller in length, on off. Will Young drives it along past the mid on fielder. The fielder gives it a chase but the outfield is fast enough for the ball to race away. A boundary.
On a good length, on off. Will Young taps it to point.
Full again, on off. Will Young with a solid defence.
Loopy ball, on off. Devon Conway steps out and pushes it to long off for a run.
Tossed up, on off. Blocked out.
Flighted ball, on middle. Defended on the leg side.
On the pads, nudged to mid-wicket.
Full and on leg, Will Young gets low and sweeps it to fine leg for a run.
Full and around off, Devon Conway defends it out.
Good length, on off stump. Young stands back and defends it out solidly.
Back of a length, around middle and leg. Young pulls it to deep square leg. The batters take a single.
Full length, on off. Conway defends it to cover.
FOUR! Totally dismissed. Short, on the bodyline. Conway rides with the bounce and pulls it through square leg for a boundary.
FOUR! Classy! A good bouncer, up around the helmet region. Conway stands tall and pulls it to deep square leg for another boundary. Runs are coming in thick and fast for the Kiwis.
Outside off, Conway looks to chase it but misses. 9 runs off it, a good over for New Zealand.
Floated, full and on leg. Young defends it to the leg side.
Around off, Young stays back and defends it out.
Flatter and on off. Young works it to short mid on.
Full and on off. Young presses forward and defends it back to the bowler.
Darted, on to the pads, Young clips it to square leg.
Full and on middle. Young clips it to mid-wicket. A maiden over from Mehidy Hasan.
Good length ball, outside off. Conway punches it towards gully. The man there dives to his left to make a good stop.
Full and outside off. Conway defends it out watchfully.
Flicked to mid-wicket for a single.
Length, on the pads. Young clips it to deep square leg for a single.
Fuller and outside off. Conway defends it solidly.
Full and outside off. Conway shuffles across and blocks it out.
Young moves to his half century now! Floated, full and on off. Young gets low and sweeps it to deep square leg for a single.
Around middle, defended out watchfully.
Conway defends it to cover.
FOUR! Conway is motoring along really well here. Tossed up, full and on leg. Conway gets low and sweeps it through mid-wicket for a boundary.
Full and on leg. Conway clips it to square leg and gets across for a quick single.

Just short! Tossed up, full and on middle. Young comes down the track and hits it unconvincingly, as he hopes to clear the man at mid on. The ball though bounces before the fielder and Young survives.
Length and on off, defended out.
Back of a length, outside off, Conway leaves it alone.
Length and outside off, defended out solidly.
Slightly short and outside off. Conway leaves it alone for the keeper.

NOT OUT! Back of a length, on the bodyline. Conway looks to pull it away but misses. The ball flies off the arm towards the slip cordon. The fielder there pouches it comfortably and the bowler puts in an appeal. The umpire is unmoved. Bangladesh skipper decides to take it upstairs for caught behind. The replays show there is no blade on it and it also shows that he was hit on his arm.
FOUR! Cracking shot! Short and on off. Conway pulls it through mid-wicket for an amazing boundary.
Drifing down the leg side, Young leaves it alone.
Loopy ball, on off. Will Young defends it out.

OUT! RUN OUT! Tossed up, on middle. Will Young nudges it to mid-wicket for a quick single but is sent back by Devon Conway. Najmul Hossain Shanto throws it at the keeper's end and Liton Das whips the bails off. Bangladesh put up an appeal for a run out and the umpire take it upstairs. Replay shows that Will Young's bat was on the line when the bails were whipped off. The third umpire after reviewing it several times shows out on the big screen. A lucky breakthrough for Bangladesh. He is not happy as he walks back.
Howout: run out (Najmul Hossain Shanto / Liton Das)

Commentary: Floated, full and on off. Taylor blocks it back to the bowler.
On the pads, defended to the leg side.
Tossed up, full and on off. Taylor pushes it back to the bowler.
Fuller, on off. Conway blocks it out.
Back of a length, outside off. Conway shoulders his arms at it.
Full length, on off. Conway drives it down the ground but ends up hitting the stumps at the non-striker's end.
Around off, blocked out.
Length ball, sliding down leg. Conway looks to flick it away but misses.
Good length, on off, Conway remains solid in defense.
Touch short and outside off. Taylor cuts it to cover but straight to the fielder.
Full and on off. Taylor defends it back to the bowler.
Ross Taylor gets off the mark now. Full length, on the pads. Taylor flicks it through mid-wicket for a brace.
Full and wide outside off. Taylor defends it to point off the outer half.
Fuller, on off. Taylor stays inside the crease and drives it to the left of mid on. The man there moves to that side to make a stop.
Length and on off. Taylor defends it out watchfully.
Back of a length, outside off. Conway looks to chase it away but misses.
Good length and outside off, shaping away. Conway lets it go to the keeper.
Fuller, wide outside off. Conway looks to punch it away but gets an inside edge on to the deck.
Length, outside off, left alone.
Good length, outside off. Conway defends it towards point.
Overpitched, on off. Conway works it to cover but not in the gap.
Good timing but Taylor cannot find the gap. Full and outside off. Taylor drives it towards the man at covers.
Full and outside off. Taylor punches it to covers but yet again he finds the fielder.
Length, on off, blocked out safely.
Fuller, on off. Taylor defends it back to the bowler with the full face of the blade.
Good length, outside off, Taylor defends it to cover off the outside edge.
Back of a length, outside off. Taylor cuts it through cover-point and collects a sinlge, before the fielder cuts it out.
Length and down leg. Taylor leaves it alone.
Short and outside off. Taylor shoulders his arms.
Fuller and on off. Taylor comes across and flicks it to the leg side.
On the pads, on a length. Taylor styas back and helps it towards fine leg for just a single.
Full, on off. Conway defends it out solidly.
FOUR! Wonderful shot. He moves to 88 now. Short and outside off, Conway stays on the back foot and cuts it over back backward point for a boundary. THAT WILL BE TEA ON DAY 1.
Full length and on off. Taylor defends it out solidly.
Good length and on off. Defended out watchfully.
Down leg, nudged to square leg.
Full and on leg, Taylor defends it to short mid-wicket.
On leg, Taylor clips it towards mid-wicket.
On off, blocked out.
LEG BYE! Full, on the pads, Conway misses his flick and it goes off his pads to fine leg. The batters collect a leg bye.
Outside off, Taylor leaves it alone for the keeper.
Full and outside off. Taylor looks to heave it away but misses.
On a length, outside off. Ross Taylor defends it back to the bowler.
FOUR! Length and outside off. Taylor carves it through covers for a boundary. Finally he gets it off the middle of the blade.
FOUR! Back-to-back boundaries. Short and wide outside off. Taylor hangs back and slaps it through point for another boundary.
Flighted, full and on middle. Conway flicks it to mid-wicket.
Tossed up, full and outside off. Conway defends it to cover.
Full and around off. Conway defends it back to the bowler.
Around off, Conway defends it out.
Slower one this time, outside off. Conway defends it out.
Short and on off. Conway blocks it out to safety.
Full and on off. Taylor defends it back to the bowler.
Full-length ball, on off. Taylor drives it to mid off.
Good length and outside off. Taylor leaves it alone.
Full length and outside off. Taylor slashes it towards cover for a single.
Hossain continues to bowl full, outside off. Conway blocks it towards cover.
Short ball, on the bodyline. Conway pulls it to square leg.
Around middle, Taylor flicks it towards mid-wicket.
Full and on off. Taylor drives it towards mid on for a single.
Full and on middle. Conway flicks it to mid-wicket and rotates the strike.
Full and on off. Taylor pushes it out watchfully.
Short and on off. Taylor pulls it to the leg side.
Full, around middle and leg. Taylor clips it towards mid on. No run.
FOUR! A beautiful drive by Conway and he gets into his 90s. Full and outside off. Conway leans forward and creams it through the cover region for a boundary.
Length, on the pads. Conway flicks it to mid-wicket and gets off for a quick single. The fielder has a shy at the bowler's end and scores a direct hit. Devon Conway is well in though.
Good length, on the pads. Taylor defends it to the leg side.

OUCH! A short ball, on middle and leg. Taylor looks to hook it away but misses and gets hit on his helmet. The ball balloons towards the right of the gully fielder who runs to that side but cannot complete the catch. Although the umpire signals a leg bye. So, it wouldn't have mattered even if the ball was caught.
Length, outside off. Conway pushes it to the off side.
Fuller and outside off. Conway drives it to cover. But not in the gap.
Tossed up, full and on middle. Taylor flicks it to the leg side.
On the pads, flicked to square leg.
Flatter and on leg. Taylor clips it to square leg and rotates the strike.
Flighted, full and down leg. Conway clips it to square leg for a run.
Tossed up, full and on middle. Taylor clips it towards mid on.
Full and outside off. Taylor drives it towards cover. But could not find the gap.
Around middle and leg, on a length. Conway clips it to square leg but straight to the fielder.
Fuller, wide outside off. Conway lets it go through to the keeper.
Back of a length, outside off. Conway punches it through point off his back foot for a single. He moves to 96.
Length ball, on off. Taylor works it towards gully.

A huge appeal for LBW but the umpire shakes his head. Fuller, on leg. Taylor gets pinged on his pads as he looks to flick it away. Taskin Ahmed appeals but the umpire is unmoved. Clearly going down leg. Bangladesh don't opt for the review now.
Fuller and outside off. Taylor drives it to cover.
Tossed up, on off. Devon Conway presses forward and blocks it out.
He is not in a hurry here! Loopy ball, on off. Devon Conway stays solid in his defence.
Flighted ball, on middle. Devon Conway prods and blocks.
On off, punched off the back foot towards covers.
Now he comes down the track! Full and outside off, Devon Conway uses his feet and pushes it to mid on for a single.

FOUR! Nicely played! This was on a shortish length, on middle and leg. Ross Taylor gets low and sweeps it to fine leg for a boundary. He is a really good player of spin so he won't mind Mehidy Hasan bowling to him.

Nearly sneaks one through the gate! Taskin Ahmed bowls from 'round the wicket, on a good length, around off. Devon Conway hops but the ball stays low. He tucks it off the inner half to square leg for a single. Moves to 98!
Short and wide, Ross Taylor cuts it through covers for a couple of runs.
Good-length ball, on off. Ross Taylor covers the stumps and pushes it past the bowler.
Fuller this time, on off. Ross Taylor wrists it to mid on.
Full again, outside off. Driven to mid off.
FOUR! Easy picking! Width on offer, outside off. Ross Taylor stays back and scythes it past backward point for a boundary. Opens the face of the bat and plays it late. Good timing on that one.
Devon Conway calls for two but settles for a single! Loopy ball, on middle. Devon Conway sweeps it to fine leg for a single. He wanted the second run but wasn't there. On 99!
Loopy ball, on middle. Ross Taylor blocks it out.
Full and on middle, pushed to mid on.
Loopy ball, on middle. Ross Taylor nudges it on the leg side. Hands over the strike to Devon Conway.
Drives but can't get it through! Full and on middle, Devon Conway drives it back to the bowler.
He will have to wait for a few more minutes! This was short and on off, Devon Conway plays it to mid on.
Fuller in length, right into the blockhole, on off. Ross Taylor jams it out back to the bowler.
Short and wide, outside off. Ross Taylor slashes it through cover-point for a single. Devon Conway back on strike.

CENTURY! There comes the single! Abosultely magnificent from him. Comes back from the injury and he produces a gem of a knock. A fantastic find for New Zealand. The crowd are up to their feet and Conway removes his helmet, raises his bat and soaks applause. Coming to the ball, this was short, on middle. Devon Conway pulls it to fine leg for a single. His second Test century and the southpaw will look to continue to build on this.
FOUR! Top Shot. Ross Taylor is motoring along really well here. A short ball, on off. Taylo pulls it to deep square leg for a boundary.
Back of a length, outside off. Taylor looks to chase it but misses.
Bangs a short ball, on middle. Ross Taylor tries to pull but misses.
Gets one to come back! Good-length ball, outside off, coming back in. Devon Conway looks to defend but the ball sneaks past the inside edge.
Short of a length, outside off. Punched off the back foot towards covers.
Length ball, outside off. Devon Conway taps it to point for a single. 50-run partnership comes up between these two now.

OUT! CAUGHT! Bangladesh have got Taylor! Dragged him into an expansive drive and he perishes. Shoriful Islam has been pick of the bowlers and he gets another wicket. This was fuller, outside off. Ross Taylor reaches out for it and drives it towards covers. This is a shot that he plays really well but this time, he finds the fielder. Shadman Islam takes a good low catch moving to his left and Bangladesh have got a crucial breakthrough.
Howout: c Shadman Islam b Shoriful Islam

Commentary: Movement there off the seam again! Back of a length, outside off, jagging back in. Henry Nicholls shoulders arms.
Another good-length ball, outside off, nipping in. Henry Nicholls lunges and raises his bat. Tidy stuff from Shoriful Islam.
Fuller, on off. Conway drives it to long off for a run.
Loopy ball, on off. Henry Nicholls presses forward to block it out.
Shortish, on off. Henry Nicholls works it to mid on.

Off the mark but in a risky manner! Flatter, full and on middle. Henry Nicholls gets down on one knee and looks to sweep. The ball goes off the top edge and fortunately for him, goes above the first slip fielder and falls in no man's land. Could have gone anywhere. A single.
This is pushed towards covers.
Full and on middle. Defended out.
Good length, outside off. Nicholls gets across and defends it out.
Back of a length, outside off, shaping in. Nicholls leaves it alone.
Good length, outside off. Nicholls leaves it alone.
Short, around the ribs. Nicholls looks to pull it away but does not middle it.
FOUR! Short and punished. Back of a length, on the bodyline. Nicholls swivels on the back foot and pulls it through deep square leg for a boundary.
Back of a length, sliding down leg. Nicholls hangs back and looks to help it around the corner but misses.
Flighted, full and on leg. Conway comes down the track and defends it to the leg side.
Fuller, outside off. Conway drives it towards cover.
Outside off, Conway punches it point for a single.
On off, blocked out.
Full and on off. Nicholls flicks it towards mid on.
Tossed up, on off. Nicholls presses forward and defends it onto the pitch.
Another dot. Length ball, on the stumps. Conway strides forward and defends it to the leg side off the inner half.
Two dots in a row! On a length, outside off. Conway leaves it alone for the keeper.
Full and outside off. Conway pushes it to covers.
Short ball, on off. Conway pulls it towards deep square leg for a single.
Length ball, wide outside off. Nicholls slaps it towards point but cannot evade the man stationed there.
Short ball, around off. Nicholls sways away from the line of the delivery.
Full and on off. Conway drives it through the cover region and gets a single.
Flighted full and on off. Henry Nicholls defends it back to the bowler.
Around off, defended to covers.
Full and around off. Nicholls blocks it back to the bowler.
Flighted, full and on leg. Nicholls comes forward and flicks it to short mid on.
Around middle, defended out.
Flatter, on middle. Devon Conway plays it to mid on.
That is well played in the end! Devon Conway looks to sweep but sees the ball is a little shortish, so he dabs it at the last moment past the first slip fielder for a couple of runs.
Short and wide, Devon Conway slaps it to sweeper cover for a single.
BYE! Sliding down leg, Nicholls misses his flick, even the keeper fails to grab it. The batters collect a bye.
On off, blocked out.
Short and outside off. Conway cuts it towards point.
Full and on off, driven to cover.
Tossed up, around off. Nicholls defends it back to the bowler.
FOUR! Good use of the feet here. Floated, full and on middle. Nicholls comes down the track and lofts it towards long on for a boundary.
Henry Nicholls uses his feet and works it to wide of mid on.
Around middle and leg. Nicholls blocks it out to the leg side.
FOUR! Second boundary of the over. Nicholls making his intentions clear. Full and on off. Nicholls lofts it over mid on and bags a boundary.
Short and outside off. Conway cuts it towards point.
FOUR! This one races away. Short and on off. Conway swivels on the back foot and pulls it through mid-wicket for a boundary.
On off, pushed towards cover for a run.
Looped up, outside off. Nicholls drives it to cover for a single.
Flatter and outside off. Conway pushes it out.
A single as this is worked towards long on.
Loopy ball, on middle and leg. Devon Conway looks to flick but misses.
Tossed up, on middle. Devon Conway clips it to square leg.
Flatter, outside off. Devon Conway lunges forward to defenf but the ball hits the pads first. Very optimistic appeal from Mominul Haque for an lbw.
On middle, blocked out.
Flatter ball, on leg. Devon Conway sweeps it to long leg for a single.
A tidy start from Mominul Haque. Short and on off, Henry Nicholls punches it to mid on off the back foot.
FOUR! Great shot! Loopy ball, on middle and leg. Devon Conway brings out the reverse sweep and hits it very well. The ball races away behind square on the leg side for a boundary.
This is pushed back to the bowler.
Loopy ball, outside off. Devon Conway pushes it to covers.
On off, Devon Conway drives it to long off for a single.
Flatter delivery, on the pads. Henry Nicholls paddles it down to fine leg for a single.
Flighted ball, outside off. Devon Conway dabs it to short third man.
Shortish, on off. Henry Nicholls defends it out.
On middle, Henry Nicholls drags it down to long on for a single.
Full, on the pads. Devon Conway clips it to square leg.
Outside off, Devon Conway is solid in his defence.
Reverse sweep again! Flatter ball, on middle. Devon Conway reverse-sweeps it to deep square leg. He wants to come back for second but is sent back by his partner. Settles for a single.
Henry Nicholls uses his feet and whips this full ball to mid on.
Tossed up, outside off. Devon Conway presses forward and defends it out.
Full and on middle, pushed to mid on.

Top edge but just short of the deep square leg fielder! Tossed up, on middle. Devon Conway looks to sweep. The ball goes off the top edge and flies towards deep square leg but falls just short. Taskin Ahmed there carries it on a bounce and the batters take a single.
On off, Henry Nicholls chops it off the underdge to point.
Flatter ball, on middle. Henry Nicholls looks to sweep but misses. He gets hit on the grill of the helmet.
Loopy ball, on off. Henry Nicholls defends it out watchfully.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Devon Conway walks back dejected. He knows that is possibly the worst way he could have gotten out. Mominul Haque drifts this down the leg side. Devon Conway looks to tickle it but the ball catches the inside edge and Liton Das behind the stumps makes no mistake. He straightaway starts celebrating and the umpire raises his finger as well. Mominul Haque has got his man and now would look to build on this.
Howout: c Liton Das b Mominul Haque

Commentary: On off, Tom Blundell blocks it out.
Flighted ball, on off. Tom Blundell looks to defend but the ball goes off the outside edge past the first slip fielder for a single.
Loopy ball, on off. Henry Nicholls punches it to long off for a single.
Angling in, on off. Tom Blundell lifts his bat a little too late and the ball hits his arms and goes back to the keeper.
Loopy ball, on off. Tom Blundell gets forward and blocks it out.
Good length, outside off, shaping away. Nicholls leaves it alone.
FOUR! Cut away! Short and outside off. Nicholls stays on the back foot and cuts it through point for a boundary.
Length ball, down the leg side. Henry Nicholls looks to flick but misses.
Back of a length, on off. Henry Nicholls stands up on his toes and defends it back to the bowler.
Wide again from Shoriful Islam! Short and outside off. Left alone.
Good-length ball, outside off, shaping away. Henry Nicholls shoulders arms.
Well outside off. No trouble for the batsman. Tom Blundell lets it be.
Again! Outside enough for Tom Blundell to make a leave.
Fuller, outside off. Tom Blundell shoulders arms to that one. The length is perfect there but Bangladesh should make the batter play more with the new cherry as there is seam movement available.
Fuller in length, on off. Tom Blundell defends it out off the back foot.
Good-length ball, outside off, nipping away. Tom Blundell with an easy leave.
Just like that! Much better from Taskin Ahmed! On a good length, around off, shaping in. Tom Blundell covers the line and blocks it out.
Nice line and length! On a good length, on off. Henry Nicholls looks to defend coming forward. The ball goes off the inner half to mid-wicket.
Outside off, on a good length. Henry Nicholls lets it sail through.
Bangs a bumper now, on leg. Henry Nicholls leaves that one alone.
Full and on off. Driven back to the bowler.
On a length, on leg. Henry Nicholls tickles it to fine leg for a run.
Good-length ball, on middle. Tom Blundell nudges it to the leg side.
FOUR! Good timing! On the pads, Henry Nicholls clips it to deep square leg for a boundary.
In the fourth stump channel, on a length. Henry Nicholls leaves it for the keeper to collect.

WIDE! Full and way outside off, outside the tramline as well. Liton Das does really well to dive full stretch to his left and stop the ball. The ball went to the second slip trajectory. It was that wide.
On a good length, outside off. Henry Nicholls shoulders arms.
Bangs a bouncer, on middle. Henry Nicholls sits under it.

Taskin Ahmed switches to 'round the wicket, bowls it on a good length, outside off. Henry Nicholls looks to punch it away from the body but misses. Taskin Ahmed and Co. are very confident though and appeal for a caught behind. The umpire says no. Bangladesh challenge the umpire. UltraEdge shows no bat involved as there was a flat line when the ball passes the bat. Bangladesh lose another review here.
Good-length outside off. Left alone.
Good length and just outside off. Blundell defends it out.
Good-length ball, outside off. Tom Blundell defends towards covers.
On a good length, on leg. Tom Blundell misses his glance. The ball hits his pads and goes to short fine leg for a leg bye.
Full and on middle, Henry Nicholls flicks it to deep mid-wicket for three runs.
FOUR! First boundary for Tom Blundell! Short of a length, on middle. Tom Blundell rides the bounce well and pulls it to deep square leg for a boundary. Well-controlled shot that.
Length ball, on middle. Tom Blundell meets it with a dead bat.
Good-length ball, outside off. Left alone.
Length ball, on middle, angling in. Henry Nicholls looks to flick but gets an inside edge onto the pads. Taskin Ahmed pleads the umpire for an lbw but the umpire is unmoved.

Nearly chopped on! Length ball, outside off. Henry Nicholls looks to drive. The ball goes off the inside edge past the stumps to fine leg for a single. Wouldn't have mattered anyway as Taskin Ahmed has overstepped by a big margin. No ball called.
On a length, outside off. Tom Blundell leaves it alone.
Length ball, outside off, shaping away. Tom Blundell lets it be.
Fuller in length, on off, with a hint of away movement. Tom Blundell knocks it back to the bowler.
Down the leg side, Tom Blundell leaves it alone.
Given some loop, outside off. Henry Nicholls drives it towards covers.
Loopy ball, outside off. Henry Nicholls shoulders arms.
Angling in, on middle. Henry Nicholls sweeps it to deep square leg for a single. 250 up for New Zealand!
Tossed up, on off. Tom Blundell defends it out.
That spun a long way! Lands on middle and turns away, down leg. Tom Blundell looks to tuck but misses.
FOUR! Nice way to end the over! This was down the leg side. Tom Blundell glances it to fine leg for a boundary. Easy pickings for Blundell.
WIDE! A loosener from Ebadot Hossain. Short and well outside off. Left alone. Wided.
Back of a length, on off. Henry Nicholls punches it to cover for a quick single. The fielder scores a direct hit at the bowler's end but Henry Nicholls was comfortably home. Good fielding though.
Short of a length again, on off. Tom Blundell pulls it to deep mid-wicket for a brace.

OUT! CHOPPED ON! Bangladesh do get a wicket in the final over of the day. Back of a length, outside off, Tom Blundell stands up on his toes and looks to punch. Plays a little late as the ball goes off the inside edge and goes back to disturb the stumps. Bangladesh would have loved a couple of wickets in the final session and they have got exactly that. Tom Blundell walks back dejected. THAT WILL BE STUMPS ON DAY 1!
Howout: b Ebadot Hossain

Commentary: Length and on off. Ravindra defends it to cover.
Fuller and outside off. Ravindra blocks it out.
FOUR! Crunched! Very full and on off. Rachin Ravindra creams it through covers and bags a boundary.
Good length, on off. Nicholls blocks it to cover.
Fuller, outside off. Nicholls drives it to cover but not in the gap.
Around off, blocked out solidly.
Length and on off. Henry Nicholls defends it to the leg side.
On a good length, much straighter, on off. Henry Nicholls defends it on the leg side.
Good-length ball, nipping away, outside off. Henry Nicholls lets it be.
Full, going down leg. Rachin Ravindra looks to flick it away but misses.
Good length, outside off, left alone.
Full length, around off, swinging in. Rachin Ravindra blocks it out solidly.
Back of a length, outside off. Ravindra leaves it alone.
BEATEN! Good length, angling across the left-hander. This one holds its line. Rachin Ravindra looks to push it through the off side but misses.
A maiden! Good length, outside off, Ravindra leaves it alone for the keeper.
Back of a length, outside off. Henry Nicholls defends it back to the bowler.
Outside off, left alone.
Short ball, outside off, shaping away. Henry Nicholls has no interest in playing that one.
Good length, outside off, moving away. Nicholls leaves it alone for the keeper.
Length, on off. Henry Nicholls presses forward and defends it out.
Length ball, on off. Henry Nicholls pushes it towards mid off.
Fullish length, outside off. With some extra bounce. Rachin Ravindra shoulders his arms at it.
Good length, on off. Rachin Ravindra blocks it out watchfully.
Short ball, outside off. Left alone by Rachin Ravindra.
Good length, wide outside off, shapes in a little late. Rachin Ravindra watches it sail past him.
Back of a length, outside off, nips in a bit. This is close to Rachin Ravindra but he shoulders his arms and did not get tempted by it.
A well directed bouncer this time, around off. Rachin Ravindra ducks under it. A maiden for Taskin Ahmed.
Short ball, outside off. Henry Nicholls leaves it alone.
Good length, outside off. Henry Nicholls stays on the back foot and cuts it to backward point but not in the gap.
First runs after 4 maiden overs. Fuller, on the pads. Henry Nicholls clips it through mid-wicket. The batters take three.
BEATEN! Good length, outside off. Rachin Ravindra looks to drive it away but misses. Shoriful Islam is doing the right thing here by enticing the batter to play outside off.
Good length, outside off. Rachin Ravindra leaves it alone.

OUT! CAUGHT! A brilliant start by the visitors. This is the start they were looking for and it is Shoriful Islam yet again who does the damage. He picks up his third wicet of the game. A length ball, outside off. Rachin Ravindra presses forward and looks to drive it to cover but only gets an outside edge. Shadman Islam at third slip takes a good catch.
Howout: c Shadman Islam b Shoriful Islam

Commentary: Length, on off, blocked out.
On a length, outside off. Henry Nicholls shoulders arms.
FOUR! Up and over! Back of a length, outside off. Nicholls stays on the back foot and cuts it over slip cordon for a boundary at third man.
LEG BYE! Length, on the pads. Henry Nicholls looks to flicks it away but misses. The ball goes towards fine leg off the pads. The batters collect a leg bye.
Full length, around leg, shaping in. Kyle Jamieson gets pinged on his pads. Taskin Ahmed makes a stifled appeal but the umpire is not interested.
Full, around middle and leg. Kyle Jamieson drives it towards mid on but the fielder there does well to make the stop.
Back of a length, outside off. Nicholls shoulders his arms at it.
Outside off, left alone.
Full and on leg. Nicholls defends it to mid-wicket.

FOUR! A really tough chance for Liton Das behind the stumps. Henry Nicholls gets lucky this time. Back of a length, on middle. Henry Nicholls stays back and looks to pull it away. It goes to the right of the keeper off the outside edge. Liton Das makes a full stretched dive to his right but the ball manages to evade him and runs into the fence at fine leg.
Good length, around off, shaping in. Henry Nicholls looks to defend it out but gets hit on his pads.
Full, on leg. Nicholls flicks it to square leg for a single.
Fuller in length, outside off. Henry Nicholls drives it to point.
Full, on the pads. Henry Nicholls clips it to square leg for a single.
Short ball, outside off, Kyle Jamieson leaves it alone without any hesitation.
This time Kyle Jamieson could not resist himself. Full length, wide outside off. Kyle Jamieson looks to go for the booming drive but gets beaten on the outside edge.
FOUR! Kyle Jamieson gets off the mark with a boundary. Full length, outside off. Kyle Jamieson prods and drives it through covers for a boundary.
Outside off, left alone by Jamieson.
Length ball, on off. Nicholls blocks it out solidly.
Short ball, on off. Henry Nicholls ducks under this one.
Back of a length, outside off, nipping away. Henry Nicholls has no interest in playing that one.
Length, on off. Henry Nicholls defends it back to the bowler.
Back of a length, on leg. Henry Nicholls stays back and pulls it to deep square leg for a single.
On a length, around off. Kyle Jamieson defends it towards short mid off. Just a single off it. A good over by Islam.
Full length, on off, shaping in. Henry Nicholls flicks it towards mid-wicket.
WIDE! Back of a length, outside off, shaping away. Henry Nicholls leaves it alone. Wide called.

FOUR! A fantastic way to get to FIFTY! There were shouts of catch it but he hit it so well that it raced away towards the fence. Short ball, around middle and leg. Henry Nicholls pulls it in front of square on the leg side and bags a boundary.
FOUR! Back-to-back boundaries. Length ball, outside off. Henry Nicholls reaches out and guides it to third man for a boundary.

FOUR! Third consecutive boundary for Henry Nicholls. This is what his side needs at the moment. Good length, outside off. Henry Nicholls stays on the back foot and cuts it through point to bag a boundary.
Outside off, left alone.
Short ball, outside off. Nicholls shoulders his arms at it.
Full and outside off. Kyle Jamieson gets it to gully off the outside edge. The man there dives to his right to make the stop.
Length ball, outside off, shaping in. Kyle Jamieson blocks it out solidly.
A sharp bouncer, on off. Kyle Jamieson ducks under this one.
Tap and run! Length ball, on off. Kyle Jamieson works it towards cover for a quick single.
On a length, on top of off. Henry Nicholls stays inside the crease and defends it out to the leg side.
Back of a length, on middle. Henry Nicholls leaves it alone.
Flighted, full and on off. Kyle Jamieson prods and blocks it back to the bowler.
On the pads, tucked to the leg side.
DROPPED! It was a tough chance for the short leg fielder. Floated, full, around middle and leg. Kyle Jamieson gets an inside edge but the man at short leg fails to gather it.
On off, pushed away.
Full, on the pads. Jamieson clips it to the leg side.
Around off, blocked out solidly.
Back of a length, on middle. Henry Nicholls ducks under it.
Short ball, outside off. Henry Nicholls leaves it alone. Liton Das leaps and make a half stop.
Touch short, on the pads. Taskin Ahmed flicks it to deep square leg for just a single.
Full and on leg. Kyle Jamieson stays back and clips it to deep mid-wicket for a run.
Outside off, tapped towards point.
Back of a length, around off. Henry Nicholls sways away from the line of the delivery.
Loopy ball, outside off. Kyle Jamieson blocks it out off the back foot.

OUT! CAUGHT! Mehidy Hasan bags his first wicket of this match. Kyle Jamieson tries to go downtown but holes out. Tossed up nicely, on middle. Kyle Jamieson advances down the track and smashes it towards long on. Not enough power on that one and Shadman Islam there completes the catch easily.
Howout: c Shadman Islam b Mehidy Hasan

Commentary: Shortish, on off. Henry Nicholls punches it to long on for a run.
Fuller and quicker, on off. Tim Southee defends it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, on middle, turning in. Tim Southee tucks it on the leg side for a single.
Flatter, angling in on the pads from 'round the wicket. Henry Nicholls defends it on the leg side.
FOUR! Dispatched! Stand and deliver stuff from New Zealand seamer. Short of a length, outside off. Tim Southee stands tall and cuts it through point for a boundary.
Good-length ball, on off. Tim Southee defends it back to the bowler.
A loud appeal for an lbw but not given! On a good length, angling in, on middle. Tim Southee looks to work it on the leg side but misses. He gets hit on the pads. Height was the issue there.
Bangs a short ball, on middle. Tim Southee sits under it.
On the pads, Tim Southee flicks it to square leg for one.
FOUR! Nicely played! Henry Nicholls moves to the leg side, Taskin Ahmed bowls a short ball, on leg. Henry Nicholls slaps it over point and bags a boundary.
Full and on off, pushed back to the bowler.
Loopy ball, on middle. Tim Southee defends it off the outer half of his bat to the off side.
Tim Southee skips down on this occasion but can't beat the mid on fielder.
Tossed up, outside off. Tim Southee leaves it alone.
Flatter, on middle. Tim Southee stays solid in his defence.
A maiden! Floats it up, on off. Tim Southee hangs back and knocks it back to the bowler.
On a good length, around off. Henry Nicholls prods and defends it out.
FOUR! Crunched! Too short, on off. Henry Nicholls pulls it with disdain to deep mid-wicket for a boundary. Bangladesh needs to get their tactics right. Can't bowl short to this guy.
Full and on middle, clipped to mid-wicket.
Good-length ball, on off. Henry Nicholls pats it back to the bowler.
Good running! On a length, outside off. Henry Nicholls punches it through cover-point for a couple of runs.
Keeps the strike for the next over! Short of a length, on off. Henry Nicholls pulls it to deep square leg for a single.
On off, Henry Nicholls flicks it to mid-wicket and is happy to take the single.
Full and outside off. Tim Southee pushes it to mid off.
On the pads, nudged to mid-wicket.

OUT! TAKEN! Mehidy Hasan gets another wicket. Flighted delivery, on middle. Tim Southee comes down the track and tries to go over mid-wicket. Instead chips it straight to the fielder. Mominul Haque jumps and takes the catch over his head. Can Bangladesh restrict New Zealand under 350?
Howout: c Mominul Haque b Mehidy Hasan

Commentary: OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Tossed up nicely, around off, spinning away. Neil Wagner lunges forward and tries to block. The ball goes off the outside edge and Liton Das takes the catch. Bangladesh appeals for it but the umpire is unmoved. They are very confident that there was an edge there. Mominul Haque challenges the umpire. UltraEdge shows there was a spike when the ball passed the bat. Excellent review from Bangladesh. So, Neil Wagner walks back for a golden duck. Mehidy Hasan is on a hat-trick now.
Howout: c Liton Das b Mehidy Hasan

Commentary: Trent Boult does well to negotiate the hat-trick ball. Full and outside off. Trent Boult defends it out.
Sprays this one down the leg side, Henry Nicholls looks to flick but misses.
Slower and fuller, on off. Henry Nicholls defends it to square leg.
Down the leg side again. Henry Nicholls misses his flick.
On leg, flicked to mid-wicket.
Full and on the pads. Nicholls flicks it to square leg for a single.
Flatter and outside off. Boult defends it out solidly.
Tossed up, outside off. Henry Nicholls punches it back to the bowler.
Outside off, cut to deep point for a run.
FOUR! Shouts of catch it but goes over the man. Loopy ball, on middle. Trent Boult dances down the track and smashes it over mid on for a boundary.
Tossed up, on middle. Trent Boult pushes it past the bowler for a run.
Flatter and fuller, on middle. Henry Nicholls drives it past mid off for a single.

DROPPED AND FOUR! Loopy ball, on middle. Trent Boult again advances and lifts it over the bowler's head towards long off. Shadman Islam there runs to his left to take the catch but puts it down. To make things worst, the ball rolls away over the ropes. Trent Boult survives.

OUT! TAKEN! Mominul Haque gets the final wicket to end New Zealand's innings. Tossed up, on middle. Henry Nicholls goes for the reverse sweep but couldn't get past backward point. Shadman Islam this time shows good reflexes and grabs it. NEW ZEALAND HAVE BEEN BOWLED OUT FOR 328!
Howout: c Shadman Islam b Mominul Haque

Commentary: Tim Southee starts with a length ball, outside off, nipping away. Shadman Islam shoulders arms to it.
Length ball, on middle, coming back in this time. Shadman Islam flicks it behind square on the leg side for a single. Bangladesh are underway!
Fuller and straighter, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy works it to mid-wicket.
Full again, outside off, shaping away. Mahmudul Hasan Joy reaches out for it and blocks it out.
Length ball, around off, nipping away. Mahmudul Hasan Joy with a solid block.
WIDE! Bangs a short ball, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy ducks underneath. Wide called for height.
Good-length ball, on off, swinging away. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it out off the front foot.
Boult starts with a back-of-a-length ball, on off. Shadman Islam defends it towards covers.
Bouncer from Boult, on middle. Shadman Islam sits under it.
Good bowling! Good-length ball, shaping away from off. Shadman Islam looks to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Back of a length, outside off, nipping away. Shadman Islam watches the ball go past him.
Good-length ball, on top of off. Shadman Islam stands up on his toes and taps it to point.

Edged but just short! Lovely piece of bowling from Boult! Good-length ball, on off, shaping away. Shadman Islam tries to defend. The ball goes off the outside edge but falls just short of Tim Southee at third slip.
Fullish, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to defend. The ball goes off the inside edge and rolls back past the stumps.
Length ball, outside off, shaping away. Mahmudul Hasan Joy shoulders arms.
Nicely played! Fuller in length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leans onto it and drives it through covers. Neil Wagner gives it a chase and keeps it down to three runs.
Good-length ball, outside off. Shadman Islam with an easy leave.
Length ball, in the fourth stump channel. Shadman Islam with a solid defence.
Length ball, outside off. Shadman Islam watches the ball closely and lets it sail through. THAT WILL BE LUNCH ON DAY 2!
Good-length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy lets it sail through.
On a good length, coming back in, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy nudges it to mid-wicket.
Short of a length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy hops and blocks it out.
FOUR! Nicely played! Trent Boult sprays this one on the pads, Mahmudul Hasan Joy tickles it down to fine leg for a boundary.
Fuller, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leaves it alone.
On a length, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets forward and blocks it out.
That one shaped nicely! Good-length ball, nipping away, on leg. Shadman Islam looks to flick but misses.
Good timing and good running! Length ball, on middle. Shadman Islam flicks it through mid-wicket for three runs.
Too straight, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets across and flicks it to deep mid-wicket for a couple of runs.
Goes wide of the crease and bowls a length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy shoulders arms.
Bangs a short ball, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy sits under it.
Down the leg side, Mahmudul Hasan Joy misses his flick.
Short of a length, outside off. Shadman Islam slashes it through extra cover for three runs.
Back of a length, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it out from the crease.
On a good length, on middle, nipping in. Mahmudul Hasan Joy nudges it to mid-wicket for a single.
Bangs a short ball, on middle. Shadman Islam ducks under it.
FOUR! Good aggressive shot that! Short of a length, on middle. Shadman Islam pulls it to deep mid-wicket for a boundary.
Good-length ball, on middle. Shadman Islam blocks it out.
Beaten! Good-length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks for the expansive drive but the ball zips past the outside edge.
On a good length, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it out.
Outside off, Mahmudul Hasan Joy leaves it for the keeper to collect.
Down the leg side, Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to flick but misses.
On a good length, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy tucks it on the leg side for a single.
On a good length, outside off. Shadman Islam pushes it through covers for a couple of runs.
On a good length, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy tickles it to fine leg for a single.
On a length, on off. Shadman Islam blocks it out.
Good-length ball, outside off. Shadman Islam lets it sail through.
On a good length, on off. Shadman Islam blocks it out.
Back of a length, on off. Shadman Islam defends it solidly.
Fullish, on off. Shadman Islam is very solid in his defence.
Good length but down the leg side, Mahmudul Hasan Joy leaves it untouched.
On the pads, this is flicked to deep mid-wicket for a single.
Good-length ball from 'round the wicket, outside off. Shadman Islam shoulders arms.
Back of a length, outside off. Shadman Islam punches it towards covers.
Nicely pulled! Short of a length, on middle. Shadman Islam pulls it to deep square leg for a single.

Sprays another delivery down the leg side. Mahmudul Hasan Joy misses his flick. Southee clearly struggling for rhythm in this spell. Might not be a bad idea to give him a break. New Zealand will need to optimise the new ball.
Nearly chopped it on! Length ball, outside off. Shadman Islam looks to drive. The ball goes off the inside edge past the sumps to fine leg for a single.
Short ball, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy ducks under it.
Short of a length, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it from the crease.
Back of a length, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy tucks it on the leg side.
Good-length ball, coming back in, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy clips it to short leg.
Fuller, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to drive. The ball goes off the inner half to mid-wicket.
Starts with a good-length ball, outside off, moving away. Shadman Islam taps it through backward point for a single.
Back of a length, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy works it on the leg side for a single.
Back of a length again, on middle. Shadman Islam does well to block it out.
Angling across the left-hander, outside off. Shadman Islam pushes it towards covers.
Good-length ball, outside off, angling away. Shadman Islam with an easy leave.
On the pads, Shadman Islam tickles it one-handed to fine leg for a run.
Back of a length from 'round the wicket, on off. Shadman Islam looks to work it on the leg side but misses. Gets hit near the box.
Same line and length from Tim Southee, Shadman Islam looks to tuck it on the leg side. The ball goes off the pads and the batters take a leg bye.
Good-length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy meets it with a dead bat.
On a good length, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy covers the line and blocks it out.
Good-length ball, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it out off the front foot.
On a good length, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it to the off side. Tody stuff from Tim Southee. Looks like change of ends has worked for him. Bowled on a lot better line and lengths.
On a good length, on off. Shadman Islam defends it out.
On off, angling away. Shadman Islam defends it out.
On a length, on middle. Shadman Islam blocks it out.
Length ball, outside off, shaping away. Shadman Islam shoulders arms.
Short of a length, on middle. Shadman Islam pulls it to deep mid-wicket for a brace.
Goes full and wide, outside off. Shadman Islam lets it be.
Good-length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy shoulders arms.
Fuller in length, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets an inside edge as he tries to flick. The ball goes to mid-wicket for a single.
On off, Shadman Islam pushes it towards covers for a single.
On a length, on off. Mominul Haque blocks it out.
Fuller, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it to mid off.
An inswinger, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy works it to mid on.
Back of a length, outside off, shpaing away, Islam leaves it alone.
Length and on off. Islam blocks it out.
Length, down leg. Islam looks to flick it away but misses.
Good length, angled across the left-hander. Islam leaves it alone.
Outside off, left alone.
Full and wide outside off. Islam drives it to cover but straight to the fielder.
Good-length ball, coming back in, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it out watchfully.
Outside off, Mahmudul Hasan Joy taps it to the off side.
That swung back in sharply! Good-length ball, shaping in from off, on leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to defend but gets struck on the thigh pad. Half an appeal for an lbw but that was going down leg.

FOUR! Edgy! Good-length ball, around off, shaping away this time. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to defend. The ball goes off the outside edge though the slip cordon for a boudary. Testing times for the batters.
Length ball, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it out.
Beautifully bowled! On a good length, outside off, nipping away. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to defend. The ball whistles past the outside edge.
Full and outside off, swing straightaway. Shadman Islam with an easy leave.
Big outswinger, outside off. Shadman Islam with another easy leave.
Length ball, outside off, shaping away. Shadman Islam lets it be.
Goes full now, on leg. Shadman Islam clears his front leg and whips it to mid-wicket.
On a good length, outside off, swinging away. Shadman Islam lets it through.
Back of a length, on off. Shadman Islam taps it towards covers for a single. Excellent start for Neil Wagner. He is getting the ball to move a lot and is bowling probing line and lengths.
On the pads, tucked to fine leg for one.
An inswinger from Tim Southee, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy flicks it to mid-wicket.
Play and a miss! This time, bowls an outswinger, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy is tempted to have a push at it. The ball zips past the outside edge.
Good-length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it to the off side.
Fuller, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy with a solid defence.
Fuller in length, outside off. Well negotiated by Mahmudul Hasan Joy. Blocks it out watchfully.

OUT! CAUGHT AND BOWLED! A much-needed breakthrough for New Zealand. Neil Wagner draws the first blood here. Very full, aimed on the pads. Islam looks to flick it away but closes the face of the bat a little too early. The ball goes off the leading edge back towards the bowler. Wagner dives in front of him to complete the catch.
Howout: c & b Neil Wagner

Commentary: Welcome to the crease, says Neil Wagner! Pace and bounce on that one. Good-length, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto hops and looks to defend but gets hit near the box.
Fuller, outside off, shaping away. Najmul Hossain Shanto leaves it alone.

Edged but safe! Good-length on off, around off, shaping away. Najmul Hossain Shanto looks to defend. The ball goes off the outside edge but falls just short of the first slip fielder. He carries it on a bounce.
Back of a length, outside off. Left alone.
Good-length ball, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto shoulders arms.
Outside off, left alone.
Fuller, on the pads. Joy clips it to square leg for a single.
On off, blocked out solidly.
Good length, wide outside off. Shanto leaves it alone.
Bouncer, on off. Shanto ducks under it.
Length ball, on off. Shanto defends it out.
Length ball, on off, nipping away a tad. Mahmudul Hasan Joy does well to defend it towards point.

That looked pretty close! An inswinger, on middle and leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to flick but misses. He gets hit on the pads. Loud appeal for an lbw but the umpire says no. Neil Wagner says he heard a noise there, indicating there was an inside edge. The Kiwis don't opt for the review here but the replay shows there wasn't an inside edge there and it would have been out.
On off, blocked out.
Bangs a short ball, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy ducks under it.
Fuller, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it towards covers.
Length ball, on middle and leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to flick but gets an inside edge onto the pads.
WIDE! Short ball, on middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto leaves it alone. Wide called for height.
Short of a length, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto taps it to the off side.
Short of a length, on leg. Najmul Hossain Shanto looks to tuck but misses. He gets hit near the body. The ball rolls to the leg side and the batters take a leg bye.
Fuller in length, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it back to the bowler.
Outside off, on a length. Mahmudul Hasan Joy lets it be.
Length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it out.
Length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it through covers for a brace.
Some late swing there! Length ball, outside off, swinging away. Najmul Hossain Shanto pushes it through covers for a single.
Fuller, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leaves it alone.
Full again, on the pads. Mahmudul Hasan Joy flicks it to deep square leg for a single 50 up for Bangladesh!
Back of a length, on middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto hops and blocks it out.

Short of a length, on middle. That shoots up after pitching. Najmul Hossain Shanto is all squared up in his defence and is taken aback by the bounce. Negotiated it well in the end as he left it alone.
FOUR! Lovely shot! Fuller this time, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto drives it through covers and gets a boundary.
Length ball, around middle and leg. Joy plays it to mid-wicket off the inner half.
FOUR! Timed that beautifully. Sliding in, towards middle and leg stump. Joy flicks it through square leg for a boundary.
Back of a length, outside off. Joy sits under this one.
Full length ball, outside off. Joy works it through backward point for a brace.
Fuller, on the pads. Joy tucks it to mid-wicket and rotates the strike.
Play and a miss! This is a loose shot from Shanto. On a length, wide outside off, enticing the batter to play at it. Shanto looks to push it away from his body but misses.
Good length, outside off. Joy shoulders his arms.
Length, on the stumps. Joy stays back and defends it out solidly.
Back of a length, outside off. Joy leaves it alone.
Back of a length, on off. Joy hangs back and blocks it out solidly.
Short yet again, on off. Joy blocks it out watchfully.
Fuller and wide outside off. Joy leans in and drives it towards cover but not in the gap though.
Good length, outside off. Shanto chips it towards mid off.
Length ball, on off. Shanto defends it back to the bowler.
Back of a length, outside off. Shanto shoulders his arms at it.
BEATEN! Full length, wide outside off. Shanto tries to squeeze it out but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Fuller, around middle and leg. Shanto clips it to mid-wicket.
Fuller and wide outside off. Shanto prods and pushes it towards cover.
Back of a length, on off. Joy stays back and blocks it out.
A sharp bouncer on off. Joy ducks under it.
Back of a length, on the bodyline. Joy rides the bounce and tucks it to square leg to rotate the strike.
Fuller and outside off. Shanto pushes it to the off side.
Good length, outside off, shaping away a bit. Shanto looks to drive it through covers but misses. The ball zips past the outside edge.
Full, on leg. Shanto flicks it to fine leg for a single.
FOUR! Nicely played. Overpitched, full and on off. Shanto leans forward and pushes it through mid off for a boundary.
Length, on off, blocked out watchfully.
Full and wide outside off. Shanto looks to chase it but misses.
Length ball, on off. Shanto blocks it out solidly.
Length ball, outside off, left alone by Shanto.
Kyle Jamieson comes 'round the wicket now and serves a full-length delivery, outside off. Shanto drives it through cover-point. The batters take two before the fielder cuts it out.
Back of a length, outside off, Joy leaves it alone for the keeper.
A sharp bouncer, on leg. Joy sits under it.
Short ball, outside off. Joy slaps it towards cover but not in the gap.
Angled down leg. Joy misses his flick.
Short ball, down leg. Joy leaves it alone.
Back of a length, on top of off. Joy stays back and blocks it on to the deck off the top of the blade.
Fuller, on off. Shanto blocks it out to safety.
Outside off, left alone.
Length ball, on off. Shanto blocks it out.
Full length, outside off, Shanto leaves it alone for the keeper.
Length ball, on off. Shanto defends it off the front foot.
Full and on off. Shanto drives it towards cover.
Loopy ball, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it on the leg side.
Flatter and on leg. Joy defends it out.
Looped up, on off. Joy blocks it out safely.
Flatter ball, on the pads. Mahmudul Hasan Joy clips it to square leg for a single.
Tossed up, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto stays solid in his defence.
Tossed up, outside off. Shanto blocks it out watchfully. THAT WILL BE TEA ON DAY 2!
Full and outside off. Joy steers it towards third man for a single.
FOUR! Nicely played. Full-length ball, on the pads. Shanto clips it through square leg and bags a boundary.
Length, on off, blocked out.
Full, around middle and leg. Shanto tucks it to mid-wicket for a single.
Good length, outside off. Shanto prods and defends it out.
Back of a length, outside off. Shanto leaves it alone for the keeper.
Flatter and on leg. Shanto defends it to the leg side.
On off, defended out watchfully.
Outside off, left alone.
Around off, Shanto defends it out off the front foot.
Flatter, on middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it out.
On the pads, Najmul Hossain Shanto works it on the leg side.
Outside off, left alone by Joy.
Fuller length, on off. Joy works it to the leg side off the inner half.
Full length, on off. Roy leans in and clips it towards mid-wicket.
Short ball, outside off. Joy shoulders his arms.
Full and wide outside off. Joy slashes it towards point.
A sharp bouncer on middle, Joy ducks under it. Third maiden of the game for Boult.
Tossed up, on off. Shanto works it towards long on for a single.
Floated, full, around middle and leg. Joy presses forward and defends it out.
Back of a length, outside off. Joy goes on his back foot and cuts it towards point.
Flighted, full and outside off, turning away. Joy leaves it alone.
On off, defended out.
Full, on off. Joy defends it on to the deck.
Touch short, outside off, just a hint of swing. Shanto leaves it alone.
Fuller and outside off. Shanto drives it to covers.
On a length, outside off, Shanto punches it towards point.
Good length, moving away, outside off. Shanto lets it go for the keeper.
On a length, outside off. Shanto shoulders his arms at it.
Full, around middle and leg. Shanto clips it towards mid-wicket.
Full, on middle. Joy clips it to the leg side.
Flicked to square leg for a single.
Tossed up, on the pads. Shanto clips it towards mid-wicket.
Floated, full and on leg. Shanto flicks it aerially towards short mid-wicket. The ball lands short of the man there.
On the pads, worked to the leg side.
Full and on the pads. Shanto clips it behind square on the leg side for a brace.
Full length and wide outside off. Joy punches it through covers for a couple of runs.
Back of a length, outside off. Joy shoulders his arms at it.
Full length, on off. Joy eases it down to mid on.
Length, on the pads. Joy flicks it to mid-wicket.
FOUR! Top shot and Joy moves to 40. Full length, on the pads. Joy stays back and flicks it through square leg for a boundary.
Outside off, shaping away. Joy shoulders his arms at it.
