On a length, outside off. Shanto looks to defend it out but misses.
On the pads, clipped to mid-wicket for a single.
Outside off, left alone by Joy.
On a length, on off. Joy pushes it out.
Full length, on off. Joy defends it out solidly.
Back of a length, outside off, Joy leaves it alone for the keeper.
Boult does everything right but fails to get the edge. It was served on a length, outside off, shaping away a hint. Shanto leans in and looks to drive it away but gets beaten on the outside edge.
On off, defended out.
Full length, on off. Shanto blocks it to covers.
Length ball, on the pads. Shanto nudges it to mid-wicket.
Full and on leg. Shanto clips it towards mid-wicket.
FOUR! Glorious shot to end the over! Full length, outside off. Shanto leans in and drives it through mid on for a boundary.
Fuller, on middle and leg. Joy clips it towards mid-wicket.
Full and on off. Joy pushes it to the off side.
Full length and outside off. Joy works it towards cover.
On off, Joy defends it out off his front foot.
Back of a length, outside off. Joy hops and taps it towards point.
Fuller and outside off. Joy prods and drives it towards mid off but straight to the fielder.
Comes 'round the wicket and bowls a length ball, on middle and leg. Najmul Hossain Shanto hops and clips it to long leg for a single.
Length ball, on off, little bit of shape there. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it solidly off the front foot.
On a good length but well outside off. Left alone.
Fullish, on off, angling in. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to defend. The ball goes off the outside edge towards gully.
Good-length ball, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy covers the line and blocks it out.
On a length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy lets it sail through. Just the single from the over.
FOUR! That's lovely! Short of a length, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto stands up on his toes and eases it through cover-point for a boundary. Brings up the 50-run stand as well.
Back of a length, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto hops and defends it right under his eyes.
On middle, clipped to backward square leg for one.
Length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy offers no stroke.
Back of a length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy punches it off the back foot through covers. Gets a couple.
On a length, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it back to the bowler.
Good running! Angling in from 'round the wicket, on middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto clips it to deep square leg and straightaway calls for two. Gets it easily.
Similar line and length, clipped to mid-wicket for a single this time.
Ohh! Good bounce and carry! A jaffa from Kyle Jamieson. On a good length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy has a poke at it. The ball whizzes past the outside edge.
On a good length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy lets it through this time.
Back of a length, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it to the off side.
Sprays this one down the leg side. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leaves it alone.
Fuller in length, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto pushes it over the bowler's head for a single. Mahmudul Hasan Joy wanted to come back for the second run but was sent back.
Length ball, on middle. Nudged to mid-wicket.
On a good length, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy stays solid in his defence.
Length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it out.
Length ball, angling away, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy watchfully defends it down the pitch.

Inside edge but doesn't carry! So, so close! Length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy goes for the drive. The ball comes back in and finds the inside edge. Tom Blundell does well to dive to his left and collect the ball on a bounce. Fell just short!
Full length, outside off. Shanto punches it through point for a couple of runs.
A sharp bouncer, on middle. Shanto ducks under it watchfully.
FOUR! Whacked down the ground. An inswinging full-length delivery, on off. Shanto hangs back and drives it towards long on for a boundary.
Good length, angled across the batter. Shanto leaves it alone for the keeper this time.
In the air but gets it through the gap. Full-length ball, outside off. Shanto drives it aerially through the cover region for a brace.
Length, on off. Shanto defends it towards cover.
On a length, outside off. Joy leaves it alone for the keeper.
Good length, outside off. Joy has no stroke to offer.

FOUR! EDGY! Mahmudul Hasan Joy is riding his luck now. Full length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to drive it away but get an outside edge and goes through the slip cordon into the fence at third man.
Good length, on leg. Joy misses his flick and gets pinged high on his pads. Loud shout for an lbw but the umpire says no.
Outside off, left alone by Joy.
On a length, outside off. Joy leaves it alone for the keeper.
On a length, outside off. Shanto shoulders his arms at it.
Good length, outside off. Shanto blocks it out.
Nice leave! Good length ball, outside off. Shanto fiddles outside the stump but the ball goes into the keeper's mitts.
Back of a length, outside off. Shanto leaves it alone.
Full length and outside off. Shanto has no stroke to offer.
Length ball, outside off. Shanto pushes it to point. He wanted a quick single but Joy was wise enough to send him back.

The bat goes flying here. Floated, around leg. Joy looks to flick it away to the leg side. The ball goes off the inside edge onto the pads to the off side. While the bat slips out of his gloves and lands near the leg slip.
On off, blocked out.
Around off. Joy punches it towards point for a run.
Tossed up, around off. Shanto works it towards cover for a single.
Around off, Joy looks to chase it but misses.
Quicker and on leg. Joy misses his flick.
Back of a length, around the hips. Shanto hops and clips it towards square leg for a single.
Back of a length, on middle. Joy ducks under it.
Short and on off. Joy defends it on the bounce to short leg.
Back of a length, on middle. Joy goes back and defends it with short hands towards short leg yet again.
Wagner bowls the short one again, on the bodyline this time. Joy hops inside the crease and blocks it out.
Short again, but Joy survives yet again.
Flatter, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto presses forward to block.

SIX! What a blow from Najmul Hossain Shanto! Gets to his FIFTY in style. Tossed up, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto sits down on one knee and smashes it over deep mid-wicket for a maximum. His second Test fifty and this has been a really important knock. He would look to convert this into three digits.
On the pads, clipped to backward square leg for a run.
Flighted ball, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it uppishly towards covers.
Full and on middle. Blocked out.
Drifting it on the pads, Mahmudul Hasan Joy works it through square leg for a brace. Moves to 49!
Neil Wagner continues with his short ball stuff! Short of a length, on middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto hops and tucks it on the leg side.
FOUR! Shanto getting innovative here. Length ball, on leg. Najmul Hossain Shanto gives himself some room and carves it through point to fetch himself a boundary.

Bangs a short ball, on leg. Najmul Hossain Shanto sits under it. Wagner gives him a stare and Najmul Hossain Shanto has a smile on his face. Good from Najmul Hossain Shanto that he is keeping his nerves calm. New Zealand are desperate for a breakthrough here.
Back of a length, on middle and leg. Najmul Hossain Shanto hops and clips it behind square on the leg side for one.
Short of a length again, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks.
Short of a length, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy this time goes for the pull shot but mistimes it to mid-wicket.
Full and on off, clipped through mid-wicket for a single.
Loopy ball, outside off, spinning away. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leaves it alone.
Tossed up, on off. Pushed towards covers.
FIFTY! On off, Mahmudul Hasan Joy punches it to long off for a single. Brings up his maiden Test fifty and raises his bat to soak applause. Has been a knock of determination and grit.
On middle, defended.
Loopy ball, on middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto pushes it to short mid-wicket.
Back of a length, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy cuts it to point.
Well bowled and well played! Short of a length again, on leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy hops and does well to block it out.
Bangs a short ball, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy evades it comfortably.
This is turning out to be a good contest between bat and ball. Short, on the bodyline. Mahmudul Hasan Joy stands on his toes and defends it out.
Yet again, short, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it from the crease.
Now comes over the wicket and bangs a short ball, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy ducks under it. Maiden from Neil Wagner.
On the pads, Najmul Hossain Shanto turns it away behind square on the leg side for a single.
Short and wide, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy works it towards covers.
Full and outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy slashes it through covers. Devon Conway gives it a chase and slides to push the ball back in play. Great commitment from him and saves a run for his side.
Loopy ball, on middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto stays solid in his defence.
Tossed up, on middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto gets down on one knee and slogs it to deep mid-wicket. Shouts of catch it but the ball falls in no-mans land for a brace.
On middle, blocked out.
Short, on the bodyline. Joy glances it to square leg.
LEG BYE! Fuller, on the pads. Joy looks to flick it away but misses. It goes towards fine leg off the pads. The batters collect a leg bye.
Short ball, on middle. Shanto ducks under it.
Good length, on off. Shanto defends it out watchfully.
Short and outside off. Shanto cuts it through backward point for a brace. The stand moves to 100 runs.
Back of a length, on leg. Shanto flicks it to the leg side.
Full and on middle. Joy defends it to the leg side.
Floated, full and outside off. Joy pushes it to cover.
Short and outside off. Joy cuts it to point. Not in the gap though.
Full and on leg. Joy flicks it to mid-wicket.
On off, blocked out solidly.
Edged and runs! Floated, full and outside off. Joy throws his blade at it. It goes off the outside edge towards third man. The batters take two comfortably.
On the pads, Shanto clips it to the leg side.
Angled into the pads. Shanto tucks it to square leg for a single.
Short ball, on the body. Joy hops and glances it down to fine leg.
A sharp bouncer, on off. Joy leaves it alone.
On the pads, Joy clips it towards square leg for a single.

OUT! CAUGHT! Two wickets for New Zealand and for Neil Wagner. He is delighted and New Zealand would hope to build on this momentum. Full-length ball, outside off. Shanto gets drawn by the width and throws his bat at it. The ball takes the outside edge and goes towards the left of gully. Will Young moves to his left and takes a good catch. Just the breakthrough New Zealand were looking for and Neil Wagner doesn't disappoint.
Howout: c Will Young b Neil Wagner

Commentary: Length ball, on off. Joy blocks it out.
LEG BYE! Fuller, on the pads. Joy misses his flick and it brushes off his pads to the leg side. The batters collect a leg bye.
A length ball, around middle. Haque gets squared up and defends it to cover off the oter half.
BEATEN! Past the outside edge. Good length ball, outside off. Haque looks to defend it out but misses.
Back of a length, outside off, shaping away. Haque leaves it alone for the keeper.

FIVE RUNS! A dream ball this one. A length ball, outside off. Haque hangs his blade away from his body. The ball takes the outside edge and lands short of the man at first slip. The ball goes off his hands and goes on to hit the helmet behind the keeper. The umpire has awarded 5 runs for Bangladesh.
Back of a length, on the hips. Joy flicks it to fine leg for a single.
Outside off, shaping away. Haque looks to chase it but misses.
Length and on off. Haque blocks it out.
Outside off, shaping away. Haque leaves it alone.
A length ball, on leg. Haque defends it out.
Bouncer and on off. Haque ducks under it in time.
Fuller in length, on off. Joy pushes it to mid off.
On a good length, on middle. Joy stays solid in his defence.
Bangs a short ball, on off. Joy leaves it untouched and evades it easily.
Back of a length, on off, angling in. Joy pushes it to mid on.
Fuller, on middle. Clipped through mid-wicket for a single.
Sprays this one down leg. Mominul looks to flick but misses.
Short of a length from Wagner, on middle. Joy hops and blocks it out.
Aerial but safe! Good-length ball, on off. Joy pushes it aerially. Lucky for him that it goes through covers. The batters run two.
Short of a length, on off. Joy sways away from the line.
Short again, on middle. Joy ducks under it this time.
On a length, on middle, was a slower ball. Joy tucks it behind square on the leg side.
Back to bowling on a shorter length, outside off. Joy sways away from the line.
Back of a length, on middle. Haque hops and tucks it on the leg side. Gets off the mark with a single.
Good-length ball, on off, Joy defends it to mid-wicket.
Good length, on leg. Joy clips it to mid-wikcet for a single.
BEATEN! On a length, outside off, moving away a bit. Haque looks to chase it but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Angled into the stumps, on a length. Haque flicks it through square leg for a brace.
Fuller and on off. Haque drives it through the cover region for a couple of runs.
Full and on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it out.

Close! Length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to drive. The ball goes off the outside edge and flies towards gully. Henry Nicholls does get a hand underneath it but the ball falls just short of him. Lucky escape for Mahmudul Hasan Joy.
Pitched up, on off. Defended back to the bowler.
FOUR! Great shot! Fuller again, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it with a vertical bat past the mid on fielder for a boundary. The timing on that one was beautiful.
Length ball, Mahmudul Hasan Joy fends it to the off side.
Fullish, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy clips it to mid-wicket.
Good-length ball, on off, nipping away. Mominul Haque blocks it out.
Length ball, on off. Mominul Haque steps out and pushes it to mid on.
Nicely played! Fuller, outside off. Mominul Haque leans onto it and creams it through covers for a couple of runs. Mominul Haque wanted the third run but Mahmudul Hasan Joy sent him back.
Outside off, on a length, Mominul Haque lets it through.
Back of a length, on middle. Mominul Haque hops and blocks it down the deck.
Another one shaping away but well outside off. Mominul Haque with an easy leave.
Back of a length, outside off. Left alone.
Length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy lets it through.
On a length, on middle. Clipped to mid-wicket for a single.

Tight single! On a length, on off. Mominul Haque taps it towards covers for a quick single. The fielder has a shy at the keeper's end but misses. Hits Mahmudul Hasan Joy's left leg instead. Bangladesh wouldn't want to lose a wicket at the stroke of Stumps.

FOUR! Nearly chopped it on! Length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to push. The ball goes off the inside edge and goes past the off stump to fine leg for a boundary. He is riding his luck now. That was inches away from hitting the off stump. Well, he has been batting brilliantly and deserves a little bit of luck perhaps.
Goes wide of the crease and bowls an in-angler, on middle and leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to defend but misses and gets struck on the thigh pad.
Back of a length, on middle. Mominul Haque blocks it on the leg side.
Sprays this one down leg. Mominul Haque looks to flick but misses. Tim Southee at second slip appeals for a catch but there was nothing on it.
Same again! Kyle Jamieson is not able to get his radar right from 'round the wicket. Another length ball, going down leg. Left alone.
Much better! Good-length ball, outside off. Mominul Haque offers no shot.
On a good length, around off, coming back in. Mominul Haque watches the ball closely and make a leave. Finally getting the radar right is Kyle Jamieson.

Oh boy! That was close! Good-length ball, on middle, nipping back in. Mominul Haque looks to defend but gets beaten on the inside edge. He gets thudded on the pads. Loud shout for an lbw but the umpire says no. New Zealand players discuss whether to take the review or not and in the end, decides against it. Replay shows that the ball was going over the stumps. So good decision not to take the review. THAT WILL BE STUMPS ON DAY 2!
Neil Wagner starts off with a fullish delivery, down the leg side. Mahmudul Hasan Joy goes for the flick but misses.
Full again, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy lunges and drives this through covers for a brace. First runs of the day for Bangladesh.
Length delivery, outside off. Left alone.
Good-length delivery, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it out.
Shorter this time, down the leg side. Mahmudul Hasan Joy tucks it towards fine leg for a single.
Shaping it away this time, outside off. Mominul Haque leaves that alone.
Full, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends that one.
Fuller length again, drifting away from outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it towards mid off.
Pulling his length back this time, A length delivery, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it out.
Touch shorter this time, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy shoulders arms to it.
Beaten! A length delivery, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy lunges and goes for the drive but gets beaten on the past edge.
Length, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy taps it towards fine leg. A single to finish the over.
Good-length delivery, nipping back in on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends that one.
Touch fuller this time, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to defend but gets an outside edge towards gully.
Full, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leans and drives it through covers. Two runs taken.
Swing and a miss! Neil Wagner serves a shorter one, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy swings hard it but gets beaten as the ball drifts away from him.
Wide! Short, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy just bends a tad bit and lets it go over him. A wide called as gone over the batsman.
Fuller, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it through covers for a brace.

OUT! TAKEN! This is just what New Zealand needed. Neil Wagner strikes yet again and sends Mahmudul Hasan Joy back to the hut. Neil Wagner serves a short delivery, wide of off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy could have let this one go, but instead, he goes to chop this on the off side but could not get hold of this one and manages to just chip it to Henry Nicholls at gully, who takes an easy catch there. New Zealand have an early breakthrough and Neil Wagner has his third wicket.
Howout: c Henry Nicholls b Neil Wagner

Commentary: Kyle Jamieson serves a length ball, outside off. Mominul Haque leaves that alone, that came back in sharply.
Length, on middle. Blocked out.
Shorter outside off. Mominul Haque punches it towards point.
Length ball, outside off. Mominul Haque offers no shot on that.
Back of a length, outside off. Mominul Haque leaves it alone.
Length ball, on middle. Mominul Haque blocks it solidly. A maiden for Kyle Jamieson!
Short in length, around leg. Mushfiqur Rahim taps it towards short fine.
Back of a length, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim shoulders arms to it.
Short again, around the off pole. Mushfiqur Rahim gets on his toes and blocks it out.

Extra bounce and just falls short! Neil Wagner serves a shorter one, around the leg side. Mushfiqur Rahim looks to flick it but the ball deflects off his gloves towards short fine leg. The ball flies in the air but lands just short of the man there.
NO BALL and FOUR! Beautiful timing on that. Kyle Jamieson serves an overpitched delivery, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim leans and drives past mid off for a boundary.
Short, on the body. Blocked out.
A length ball, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim offers no shot on that.
Fuller, on middle. Mominul Haque pushes it back to the bowler.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Mominul Haque lets that go through.
Shaping it away this time, outside off. Mominul Haque leaves it alone.
Length ball, on middle. Mominul Haque blocks it out watchfully.
Touch fuller, outside off, nipping it away from Mominul Haque, who offers no shot on that.
Full, wide off. Mominul Haque lunges and drives it to mid off.
Neil Wagner serves a length ball, on the pads. Mushfiqur Rahim taps it on the leg side.
Bouncer this time! A short ball, around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim ducks underneath it.
A fuller length this time, wide of off. Mushfiqur Rahim, on front foot, leaves it alone.
Good-length delivery, on middle. Mushfiqur Rahim defends that one solidly.
A fuller length, much straighter this time, on the pads. Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it towards deep square leg for a brace.
Back of a length, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim bends and leaves it alone.

DROPPED! A tough chance goes down! Kyle Jamieson serves a fuller one, onto the pads. Mominul Haque closes the face of the bat and looks to flick, but gets a leading edge towards the bowler. Kyle Jamieson dives to his right and gets his hand to it but fails to collect it.
Beaten! A length ball, around the fourth stump line. Mominul Haque looks to defend but gets beaten past the outside edge.
A length ball, around off. Blocked out.
Tad fuller, outside off. Mominul Haque leans and defends it out on the off side.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Mominul Haque shoulders arms to it.
Length, on middle. Mominul Haque, on back foot, blocks it out.
Neil Wagner delivers a shorter one, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim ducks underneath it.
Very full, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it to mid off.
Touch shorter, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim, on his toes, blocks it out.
Short ball, over middle. Mushfiqur Rahim bends back and will lets go through.
Length ball, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out.
Shorter again, slanting across. Mushfiqur Rahim gets low and will leave it alone.
Too short on this occassion. Mominul Haque ducks under that one.
Overpitching it again, on middle. Mominul Haque digs it out towards cover.
A length ball this time, outside off. Mominul Haque pushes it towards cover point this time.
Beaten! Kyle Jamieson serves a shorter one, just outside off. Mominul Haque looks to defend but gets beaten as the ball whizzes past the outside edge.
Good-length ball, around off. Mominul Haque blocks it towards point.
Length, down the leg side this time. Mominul Haque gets on top of it and blocks it out.
Back of a length, around middle and off. Mushfiqur Rahim, on back foot, blocks it out.
Too short, around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim ducks and lets that go through to the keeper.
Back of a length, around the off pole. Mushfiqur Rahim gets low, leans back and leaves it alone.
Neil Wagner servers a good-length delivery, around the pads. Mushfiqur Rahim taps it to short fine leg.
Shortis delivery, outside off. Left alone.
Another bouncer, around middle and leg. Rahim ducks underneath it.
Flatter, outside off. Mominul Haque chops it to the man at point.
Loopy delivery, on middle. Mominul Haque leans and pushes it to short fine.
Tosses it up, outside off. Blocked out.
Shorter this time, around leg. Mominul Haque hangs back and pulls towards fine leg for a run. First runs for Mominul Haque today.
Loopy delivery, around off. Rahim defends it out.
Darting it on middle and leg this time. Mushfiqur Rahim nudges it to short fine leg.
Brilliant fielding! A full ball, outside off. Mominul Haque drives it towards covers. Devon Conway makes a diving stop and saves four runs.

NO BALL! Mominul Haque survives! Neil Wagner serves a shorter one, outside off. Mominul Haque goes for the defensive shot, but gets a slight edge back to the keeper. Umpire gives it out, but the replay rolls and shows Neil Wagner has overstepped here. Mominul Haque gets a lifeline here.
Another short ball, on middle. Mominul Haque blocks it out.
Full, outside off. Mominul Haque gets an outside edge towards gully.
Full again, outside off. Mominul Haque blocks it out.
Beaten! Length ball, outside off. Mominul Haque looks to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.
And again! This time it was even closer to the outside edge. Neil Wagner serves a length ball, outside off. Mominul Haque looks to block that, but gets beaten as the ball drifts away a tad bit.
Trent Boult starts off with a length ball, around off, Rahim defends that one.
Touch shorter, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim shoulders arms to it.
On a length, swinging it onto the pads. Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it to square leg for a single.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Mominul Haque leaves it alone.
Full and on offf. Mominul Haque blocks that but gets an inside edge back to the pads.
Swinging it away, outside off. Mominul Haque offers no shot on that.
Tim Southee starts off with a length ball, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Another length ball, shaping it away outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it towards cover.
Touch fuller, darting it on the pads. Mushfiqur Rahim leans and flicks it towards square leg for a single.
Fuller again, outside off. Mominul Haque lunges and blocks it out.
Fuller length again, around the off pole. Mominul Haque, on front foot, blocks it solidly.
Tim Southee serves another full-length ball, outside off. Mominul Haque drives it to the man at mid off. A dot to end the over.
Boult serves it o tad fuller, outside off, at 129 clicks. Mushfiqur Rahim leans and shoulders arms to it.
Touch fuller, around the pad, nipping it back in this time. Mushfiqur Rahim works it towards fine leg for a single.
Length ball, on the pads. Mominul Haque blocks it out on the leg side.
LEG BYE! Good-length ball, on the pads. Mominul Haque looks to flick but misses and the ball brushes off his pads and rolls towards fine leg. The batters steal a leg bye here.
Short ball, outside off. Left alone.
Good-length delivery, swinging it on the pads this time. Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it to square leg.
A length ball, outside off. Mominul Haque pushes it towards covers and scampers through to the other end.
Touch shorter this time, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim, on back foot, blocks it out.
Sharp bouncer, down the leg side. Mushfiqur Rahim ducks underneath that one.
On a length, outside off. Left alone.
Another good length ball, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out off the back foot.
Length ball, swinging it away outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim chops it towards cover.
Back of a length, outside off. Mominul Haque hangs back and pushes that past point for a brace. That brings up the 200 for Bangladesh!
Touch fuller this time, outside off. Mominul Haque lunges and blocks it.
Trent Boult drops it a touch shorter this time, outside off. Mominul Haque gets an inside edge on to his pads.
Fuller, around the off stump channel. Mominul Haque pushes it back to the bowler.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Mominul Haque, on back foot, blocks it out.
Length, outside off. Mominul Haque hangs back and defends it out.
A length ball, outside off, at 125.1 clicks. Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Fuller, outside off, an outswinger. Mushfiqur Rahim offers no shot.
An inswinger this time but this down the leg side. Mushfiqur Rahim looks to flick this but fails to get any bat.
A length ball, down the leg side again. Mushfiqur Rahim goes for the flick once again and misses it altogether.
A fuller ball, outside off, shaping it away this time. Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Full, on the pads. Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it towards deep mid-wicket for a brace.
Back of a length, outside off. Mominul Haque lets that go through.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Mominul Haque pushes it to point.
Back of a length, outside off. Mominul Haque leaves it alone.
Too short this time, around middle. Mominul Haque ducks underneath it and lets that go through.
A full length this time, on the pads. Mominul Haque flicks it to the man at mid-wicket.
Swinng and a miss! A shortish ball, wide of off. Mominul Haque, on back foot, looks to chop this but gets beaten as the ball shapes away from him. A dot to end the over.
Fuller in length, shaping it away from outside the off stump. Mushfiqur Rahim leans and shoulders arms to it.
Short again, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone again.
Good-length delivery, on the pads. Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it towards fine leg through the inner half of his bat.
Short of a length, outside off. Mominul Haque leaves it alone.
Fuller this time, outside off. Mominul Haque taps it towards point.
Length, on middle. Blocked out.
Full, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim leans and drives it towards cover.

OUT! CLEANED HIM UP! Trent Boult strikes and sends back an experienced player here. What a peach of a delivery to dismiss Mushfiqur Rahim. Trent Boult changes his angle, goes round the wicket, serves a very full delivery, on middle. Mushfiqur Rahim looks to flick this away but misses. The ball goes through and knocks the middle stump over.
Howout: b Trent Boult

Commentary: Length ball, outside off. Liton Das blocks it out.
Touch fuller, outside off. Liton Das leans and drives it mid off.
Sharp bouncer this time, down the leg side. Liton Das ducks underneath it.
Length ball, outside off. Liton Das, on back foot, blocks it. End of a successful over.
Length ball, nipping back in. Mominul Haque misses his glance and gets hit on pads.
Back of a length, outside off. Mominul Haque hangs back and punches it towards point.
Length, outside off. Mominul Haque leaves it alone.
Full, swinging it in. Mominul Haque looks to defend but gets an inside edge that hits the deck and bounces over the stumps.
FOUR! Edgy runs! Tim Southee serves a full ball, outside off. Mominul Haque leans and looks to drives that, but manages to get a thick outside edge past gully for four.
Outside off, on a length. Mominul Haque leaves it alone.
Nipping it back in onto the pads. Liton Das misses his flick and gets hit high on the pads.
Good-length ball, outside off. Liton Das hangs back and blocks it watchfully.
Touch fuller, darting it onto the pads. Liton Das tucks it square on the leg side for a couple of runs.
Full, swinging it in this time. Liton Das pushes it back to the bowler.
Trent Boult goes over the wicket now, serves a length ball, outside off. Liton guides it towards point.
Much straighter this time, on a length. Liton Das flicks it past backward square leg for a single.
Fuller, on the off pole. Liton Das pushes it towards mid off.
FOUR! Glorious drive! Tim Southee overpitches this one, outside off. Liton Das leans and drives it past covers for a boundary.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Liton Das taps it towards point.
FOUR! Another boundary for Liton Das! Tim Southee drops it short, on middle. Liton Das hangs back and pulls it past the square leg fielder for a boundary.
Fuller, on the pads. Liton Das knocks it to mid on.
Another full-length delivery, outside off. Liton Das looks to block this but gets a bottom edge towards the keeper.
Tad shorter, outside off. Mominul Haque, on back foot, blocks it out.
Loopy delivery, very full, on middle. Mominul Haque leans and works it away to mid-wicket for a single.
Flatter and quicker this time. Liton Das defends with soft hands and manages to get an outside edge towards point. A single taken.
Full, outside off. Mominul Haque pushes it towards mid on.
Touch shorter, outside off. Mominul Haque blocks it out.
Tosses it up this tie, outside off. Mominul Haque drives it to mid off. THAT WILL BE LUNCH ON DAY 3!

Runs straightaway for Bangladesh after lunch! Kyle Jamieson serves a short ball, outside off. Liton Das stands tall, hangs back, and punches it through covers. Will Young chases it, dives, and stops the ball from crossing the rope. Saved a single here.

NOT OUT! An appeal for LBW, but turned down. And New Zealand have gone for the review here. A full ball, darting it on the pads. Mominul Haque looks to flick but misses and gets trapped on the front pad. Umpire says no, but New Zealand go upstairs. The replay rolls in, UltaEdge confirms no bat. Ball Tracker shows it was pitching outside leg. The decision stands and New Zealand lose a review here.
Full, on the pads. Mominul Haque flicks it to fine leg for a single.
On a length, outside off. Liton Das blocks it out.
Another length delivery, outside off. Liton Das leaves it alone.
Wide! Very short on this occasion. Liton Das ducks underneath it. A wide called as the ball was way above Liton's head.
Good-length delivery, down the leg side. Liton Das misses his flick.
Beaten! A length ball, outside off. Mominul Haque looks to defend this but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Length, outside off. Left alone.
FOUR! Top-shot! Neil Wagner serves a full delivery, outside off. Mominul Haque drives it perfectly through covers for a boundary.
Another length delivery, outside off. Mominul Haque leaves it alone.
FOUR! Another four in the over for Mominul Haque! This one was darted on the pads, on a good length. Mominul Haque hangs back and flicks it towards fine leg for a boundary.
Length ball, outside off. Blocked towards mid on.
Length delivery, outside off. Left alone.
Fuller this time, outside off. Liton Das blocks it out.
Tad shorter, around off. Liton Das, on back foot, blocks it out.

Fuller in length again, on middle. Liton Das drives it towards mid off. Tom Latham fumbles there, and the ball runs towards the boundary. The ball won't go all the way, but the batters take three runs.
FOUR! Another one down the leg! Kyle Jamieson serves a length ball, down the leg side. Mominul Haque, on back foot, flicks it away towards fine leg for a boundary.

Ouch! Extra bounce and Mominul Haque is slightly hurt. A short of a length delivery, around off. Mominul Haque looks to leave that alone, but the ball deflects off his unprotected elbow area due to the extra bounce. The physio is out there to take a look.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Liton Das leans drives it to the man at cover.
Touch fuller, outside off. Liton Das lunges and blocks it out.
FOUR! A magnificent shot here! Neil Wagner overcooks this one, around off. Liton Das leans and drives it straight down the ground for a boundary. A perfect straight drive here.
Another full delivery, on the pads. Liton Das works it towards square leg for a brace.
Fuller, outside off. Liton Das pushes it towards covers.
Good-length delivery, around off. Liton Das blocks it out.
On a length, outside off. Mominul Haque shoulders arms to this one.
Touch shorter this time, outside off. Mominul Haque lets that go through.
Back of a length, again outside the off pole. Mominul Haque offers no shot on this  one.
Short of a length, on the pads. Mominul Haque flicks it uppishly towards square leg for a single.
FOUR! Beautifully driven! Kyle Jamieson overcooks this one, wide of off. Liton Das leans and drives it past covers for a glorious boundary.
Short of a length, around middle. Liton Das ducks underneath this one.
Nicely bowled! Fuller, around middle. Mominul Haque looks to block this but gets a leading-edge towards cover point.
Fuller, outside off. Mominul Haque pushes it towards cover.
Another full-length delivery, outside off. Mominul Haque lunges and blocks it out.
Beaten! A length ball, around the fifth stump line. Mominul Haque goes for his defensive shot but gets beaten on the outside edge.
And again! This is good bowling by Neil Wagner! Much fuller in length, wide of off. Mominul Haque leans and goes his drive but gets beaten altogether.
Full, on middle. Mominul Haque pushes it back to the bowler.
Short ball, around off. Liton Das hangs back and blocks it out.
Another short ball, wide of off. Liton Das slashes it towards cover point for a single.
Back of a length, outside off. Mominul Haque leaves it alone.
Very short this time, around middle and leg. Mominul Haque ducks under it.
A replica of the previous ball. Short around middle and leg. Mominul Haque ducks underneath it and lets it go.
Full, on off. Mominul Haque blocks it solidly.
Fuller, outside off. Liton Das shoulders arms to it.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Liton Das, on back foot, blocks it towards point.
Back of a length, on the body. Liton Das pulls it away towards square leg for a single. That brings up the 50 partnership between these two.
Length ball, outside off. Mominul Haque leaves it alone.
Uh-oh! Neil Wagner missed his length here and serves a slower full toss ball, outside off. Mominul Haque ducks and then tries to play the upper cut.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Left alone.
Back of a length, darted on the thigh pads. Liton Das tucks it towards square leg for a brace.
Another shorter one, angling in across off. Liton Das leaves that alone.
Short, outside off. Left alone.
Another bouncer, around middle. Mominul Haque ducks underneath this one.
Too short on this occasion, around middle. Mominul Haque ducks under it.
Fuller, outside off. Mominul Haque blocks it out.
Length ball, outside off. Liton Das shoulders arms to this one.
FOUR! In the air..but in the gap! Neil Wagner serves a full-length delivery, wide of off. Liton Das leans and drives it uppishly through covers for a boundary.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Liton Das leaves it alone.
On a length again, outside the off stump channel. Liton Das lets that go through.
FOUR! Crunched! Neil Wagner drops it short this time, on middle. Liton Das sits up and pulls this with all his power towards deep square leg for a boundary.
Length delivery, outside off. Liton Das leaves it alone.
Length and on off. Blocked out.
LEG BYE! Touch short, on leg. Haque looks to pull it away but it brushes off the pads towards fine leg. Two leg byes taken.
FOUR! Streaky and through the gap. A length ball, on off. Haque works it to third man off the outer half and gets a boundary.
On off, blocked out.
Full, on leg. Haque flicks it through square leg for a couple.
Good length, outside off, shaping away. Haque leaves it alone for the keeper.
Good length, on off blocked out.
Fuller and outside off. Das drives it towards cover.
Short and on off. Das pulls it to fine leg for a single.
FOUR! Glorious cover drive. Full-length, wide outside off. Haque leans in and drives it through the cover region for a boundary.
FOUR! Streaky this time! Length ball, outside off. Haque steers it through slip cordon for a boundary.
Length and on off. Blocked out.
Back of a length, outside off. Das defends it out watchfully.
On off, defended out.
Full and on off. Das pushes it to cover.
Short ball, around off. Das hangs back and blocks it out.
Swing and a miss! Good length, outside off. Das looks to play far from his body but misses it completely.
Sharp bouncer, outside off. Das sways away from the line of the delivery.
Touch shorter, outside off. Mominul Haque, on back foot, punches it towards cover point.
Back of a length, outside off. Mominul Haque offers no shot on that.

NOT OUT! Mominul Haque is safe! Tim Southee serves a length ball, outside off. Mominul Haque opens the face of his bat and guides it towards third man. The fielder chases it, dives and stops the ball from crossing the boundary ropes. He collects the ball and throws it to the keeper, who then whips the bails off. But, the replay rolls and confirms Liton Das's bat was inside, the dive from him has saved him here.
Short of a ball, around middle Liton Das ducks underneath it.
Another short ball, around middle and leg. Liton ducks and lets that go.
Outside off, left alone by Das.
Back of a length, outside off. Haque defends it to point.
A sharp bouncer this time, on off. Haque leaves it alone.
Fuller, on the pads. Haque flicks it towards fine leg.
Around off, pushed towards mid on.
Short and on off. Haque ducks under it and leaves it alone.

FOUR! Mominul Haque the Bangladesh skipper marches on towards his FIFTY with a boundary. He is leading from the front here. Slower one, full and outside off. Haque leans in and drives it through the cover region for a boundary.
Back of a length, on middle. Das flicks it towards square leg.
Back of a length, on the bodyline. Das sits under it.
Short ball, on off. Das pulls it through square leg for a single. He moves to 43.
Full and on off. Blocked out.
Fuller and outside off. Haque leans in and drives it through the cover region for a single.
A stifled appeal from the keeper but the umpire is unmoved. Back of a length, outside off. Das looks to cut it away but gets beaten by the bounce. Bangladesh trail by 38 runs.
Back of a length, on off. Haque blocks it out watchfully.

EDGED but doesn't carry. Back of a length, in the corridor of uncertainty. Haque hangs his blade out to defend. Boult is able to get the outside edge this time but the ball lands short of the man at first slip.
Good length, outside off. Haque defends it to cover.
Around off. Haque remains solid in his defence.
On the pads, flicked to deep square leg for a brace this time.

Flighted full and on off. Das defends it into the deck off the front foot.
Full and on off. Das blocks it out to the leg side.
On off, blocked out.
Looped up, full and on off. Das defends it out.
Outside off, some extra bounce this time. Das leaves it alone.
Full and on off. Das blocks it out solidly. A good over by Liton Das.
Fuller, on middle and leg. Haque gets his blade down in time and defends it out.
Good length and on the stumps. Haque defends it out watchfully.
LUCKY! On a length, on off. Haque looks to push it to the off side. The ball takes the inside edge and bounces over the stumps.
Full and on leg. Haque flicks it towards square leg for a single.
Length ball, outside off. Das punches it towards sweeper cover for a single.
Length ball, on middle. Haque defends it to the leg side.
Floated, full and on off. Das prods and defends it out.
Full and on off, blocked out to safety.
On off, blocked out off the front foot.
Full and on off. Das drives it to covers for a single.
Full and on middle. Haque defends it out to the leg side.
Fuller and outside off. Haque leans in and drives it towards cover.
Well bowled! Back of a length, on middle and leg. Das was caught in double mind and in the end he manages to block it out solidly.
Top delivery, very close to the gloves this time. Good-length ball, going across the right-hander. Das stays back and sways away from the line.
Around the hips, Das works it towards square leg for a single.
Slower bouncer, down leg. Haque sits under it.
Outside off, Haque leaves it alone this time.
Short ball, outside off. Haque has no stroke to offer.
Looped up, full and on off. Das prods and blocks it out.
Loopy ball, full and outside off. Das reaches out and pushes it to cover for a single.
Short and on off. Haque pulls it through square leg for a single.
Tossed up, full and on off. Das blocks it out solidly.
Looped up, full and on off. Das helps it towards mid off for a single.
Full and on off. Haque comes forward and flicks it to short mid-wicket.
Back of a length, on leg, Das pulls it towards fine leg for a single. 300 runs come up for Bangladesh.
Short and on off. Haque defends it towards cover.
A bouncer, down leg. Haque leaves it alone.
Full and on the pads. Haque clips it to the leg side.
A bouncer down leg. Haque ducks under it without any hesitation. Wagner and Haque exchange some words. Bangladesh batters have frustrated the bowlers here clearly.
On the pads, Haque flicks it towards square leg.
Flatter and on off. Das pushes it to the off side.
Flighted, full and on off. Das defends it towards cover.
Quicker, full and on off. Das blocks it out solidly.
Around off, Das remains solid in his defense.
Looped up, full and on off. Das plays it back to the bowler.
Floated, full and on off. Das defends it to the off side. He still is on 49.
Back of a length, on middle. Haque sits under this one.
Full length, on off. Haque stays back and drives it down the ground. The batters take three before the fielder cuts it out.
Back of a length, on the body. Das hops and defends it towards short leg. The umpire signals a no ball, as the bowler oversteps.
Bouncer, on off. Das leaves it alone for the keeper.
Touch short, around the hips. Das flicks it towards fine leg.
Back of a length, angled across the right-hander. Liton Das hangs back and drops his blade down in time to leave it alone.
Short ball, on leg. Das defends it out awkwardly.
Floated, full and down leg. Haque flicks it towards square leg for a single.
A brilliant innings from Das. He gets his first half-ton against the Kiwis. Short and outside off. Das hangs back and cuts it towards point for a couple.
Full and on middle. Blocked to the leg side.
Flighted, full and on off, turning away. Das leaves it alone for the keeper.
Full and on off. pushed away.
Short and outside off. Das leaves it alone watchfully. THAT WILL BE TEA ON DAY 3.
Good length, on the off stump. Haque stays back and blocks it out.
A length ball, angled in on off. Haque gets an inside edge on to the pads.

Around off, blocked out.
Full and outside off. Haque drives it to covers for a single.
Back of a length, on the body, Das blocks it to the leg side.
Around off, pushed to point for a single.
FOUR! Cut away! Short and outside off. Das stays on the back foot and cuts it through point for a boundary.
A little bit of turn this time! Outside off, turning away. Das leaves it alone.
Outside off. Das has no stroke to offer.
Full and on off. Das blocks it out solidly.
Quicker, full, around middle and leg. Das defends it into the deck.
Good length, outside off. Haque shoulders his arms.
Touch short and outside off. Haque does not entertain it at all.
Length ball, outside off. Haque hangs his blade out and defends it to the off side.
Fuller and on off. Haque flicks it to short mid-wicket.
Southee angles in a length ball into the batter on off. Haque tries to drive it down the ground but gets an inside edge onto the pads.
Full and on off. Haque defends it to the off side.
On the stumps, Das defends it to cover.
Full and on off. Das leans in and blocks it into the deck.
Looped up, full and on off. Das remains solid in his defence.
Around off, blocked out.
Full and outside off. Das leans in and drives it towards short cover.
FOUR! Easy pickings! Short and outside off. Das cuts it through backward point off his back foot for a boundary. Bangladesh trail by 7 runs now.
BEATEN! Good length, outside off. Haque stays back and looks to defend it out but misses. He gets beaten on the outside edge.
Length and on off. Haque defends it back to the bowler.
Fuller, on off. Haque flicks it to mid-wicket for a single.

SCORES LEVEL! Length ball, angled down leg. Das flicks it to fine leg and collects a brace.
Loopy delivery, outside off. Mominul Haque swivels and works it away towards fine leg for a single. Bangladesh are in the lead!
Tosses it up, on middle. Liton Das lunges and blocks it watchfully.

Almost cuts it to the slip fielder! A shorter on, outside off. Liton Das hangs back, and tries to cut through point, but gets a slight outside edge towards the first slip fielder.
Quicker this time, flatter, outside off. Liton Das leaves that alone.

On a length, down the leg side this time. Mominul Haque goes for the flick but misses.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Mominul Haque blocks it on off side.
Loopy delivery, on middle. Liton Das pushes it to the man at mid off.
Tossed up delivery on middle. Liton Das prods and blocks it out.

Loopy delivery, around middle and off. Liton Das drives it to mid off.
Another flighted delivery, outside off. Liton Das pushes it to the cover region.
Shorter, around off. Liton Das, back foot, blocks it out.
A length delivery, on the pads. Mominul Haque flicks it towards mid-wicket. A single taken.
Another good-length delivery, down the leg side. Liton Das tucks it to short fine leg.
Right in the blockhole! A yorker, on off. Liton Das jams it out on the off side.

FOUR! Up and over! Mominul Haque showing some kind of aggression here. A loopy ball, full and on middle. Mominul Haque advances down the pitch and tonks it towards deep mid-wicket for a boundary.
Loopy ball, around middle and off. Mominul Haque leans and blocks it out.
Much flatter this time, outside off. Mominul Haque, on back foot, punches it towards covers.

On the pads, tucked to square leg for a single.
Flighted, full and outside off. Das drives it aerially through covers but it lands safely.
FOUR! Full and on off. Haque clips it through square leg to find a boundary.
Full and outside off. Haque drives it to cover-point.
On a length, outside off. Haque lets it sail past him.

Good length, outside off. Haque prods and shoulders his arms.
Left alone again to see off the over. Bangladesh lead by 13 runs now.
On off, blocked out.

On a length, outside off. Haque punches it towards point.

Tossed up, on off. Haque leans in and works it to the leg side.
On middle and leg. Haque flicks it towards mid-wicket. Not in the gap though. Rachin Ravindra has been very economical but has been unable to snatch a wicket here.
Back of a length, on off. Das ducks under it.

Full and on off. Das drives it to covers.
Length and on off. Das defends it out solidly.
Good length, on off. Das defends it out.
Full length, on off. Das drives it towards cover but not in the gap.
Back of a length, outside off, left alone.
Full and outside off. Haque defends it towards cover.
Good length, on off. Haque punches it through covers for a couple now.
Length, on off. blocked out.
Full and outside off. Haque drives it towards covers.
Back of a length, outside off. Haque defends it out solidly.
Good length, outside off, nipping in. Haque leaves it alone watchfully.
Shorter, turning it away from outside off. Liton Das, on back foot, chops it to point.
Quicker, on middle and off. Liton Das blocks it out off the back foot.
Loopy ball, full, on middle. Liton Das clips it uppishly towards deep mid-wicket for a brace. That brings up 350 for Bangladesh!
Tosses it up, outside off. Left alone.
Another flighted delivery, very full, on middle. Das works it away towards short mid-wicket.
Slower through the air, full, on middle. Liton Das flicks it to mid-wicket.
Fullish length, outside off. Mominul Haque blocks it out.

Slower through the air, outside off. Liton Das hangs back and punches it towards long off. A single taken.
Loopy delivery, outside off, very full this time. Mominul Haque lunges and drives it towards cover.
Flighting it up again, around off. Blocked out by Mominul Haque.
Full, loopy delivery, on middle. Mominul Haque pushes it to mid on.
FOUR! Nicely done! Rachin Ravindra tosses this one up, on off. Mominul Haque shimmies down the pitch and drives it towards deep cover for a boundary.
Slower, around off. Mominul Haque skips down again and works it away towards mid on.
Length ball, outside off. Liton Das blocks it out solidly.
Back of a length, on middle. Das stands deep in his crease and defends it out.
Wagner drops it short again, on the middle. Liton Das pulls it to deep square leg for a single.
Shorter, outside off. Mominul Haque stands tall, and pushes it towards deep cover off the back foot. Two runs taken.
Full in length this time, angling in on off. Mominul Haque defends it solidly.
Touch fuller, outside off. Mominul Haque drives it towards mid off.
Swing and a miss! A flatter delivery, outside off. Liton Das hangs back and tries to chop that but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Loopy delivery, outside off. Das leaves that one alone.
Fuller, slower on middle. Liton Das leans and blocks it out watchfully.
Touch shorter this time, outside off. Liton Das waits back and slashes it past point for a brace.

OUT! LBW! A length ball, around off. Haque presses forward and looks to defend it out but misses and gets pinged on the pads. The umpire raises his dreaded finger. Haque takes it upstairs for a review. The UltraEdge shows no blade is involved. The Ball Tracker shows three reds and Haque has to walk back on 88. He is really dissapointed with himself.

NOT OUT! An appeal for caught behind, but the umpires says no. Trent Boult serves a length ball, outside off. Das hangs back and tries to chop that gets beaten on the outside edge as the ball seams away from him. Trent Boult is excited and appeals, but the umpire thinks otherwise.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! This time Trent Boult gets the outside edge. He strikes and gets the big wicket of Liton Das. Trent Boult serves a length ball, wide of off. Liton Das stretches for it and tries to cut that, but get a thick outside edge to the keeper. No foot movement from Liton Das, he stood there and tried fetching the ball, but failed. An exceptional innings comes to an end.
Howout: c Tom Blundell b Trent Boult
