Outside off, left alone by Ali. Boult racks up his eleventh maiden over of the innings.
A sharp bpuncer, on middle. Hasan ducks under it.
Back of a length, on the bodyline. Hasan stays inside the crease and sways away from the line of the delivery in the end.
Short ball, down leg. Hasan pulls it to fine leg off his gloves. The ball lands safely and the batters collect a brace.
FOUR! Lovely shot! Short ball, outside off. Hasan rides the bounces and punches it through point for a boundary. Lead moves to 57.
Back of a length, on off. Hasan defends it out.
Short ball, angling down leg. Hasan stays back and drags his pull shot towards fine leg for a single.
Fuller and outside off. Hasan drives it towards cover.
Length, outside off. Hasan leaves it alone.
Fuller and outside off, shaping away. Hasan leaves it alone.
Full and outside off. Hasan shoulders his arms.
Back of a length, on middle and leg. Hasan stands tall and pulls it to square leg for a run.
Good length, outside off. Ali defends it towards cover.
Short ball, outside off. Hasan leaves it alone.
FOUR! Top shot! Short and wide outside off. Hasan hops inside the crease and cuts it through point for a boundary. Hasan motoring along really well here. Lead moves to 63 now.
A hint of shape! Length and outside off, moving away, Hasan leaves it alone without any hesitation.
Full length, on off. Hasan blocks it out solidly.
Length ball, angled in on off. Hasan defends it out watchfully.
Wide outside off, Hasan has no stroke to offer.
A fuller delivery, outside off. Yasir Ali shoulders arms.
Fuller again, on middle and leg, nipping back in this time. Yasir Ali blocks it out.
Another full delivery, outside off. Yasir Ali leans and defends it out solidly.
Tim Southee misses his yorker this time, serves a low full toss ball, on the pads. Yasir Ali tucks it to the fielder at mid on.
Short ball this time, around the leg side. Yasir Ali ducks under it.
A length delivery, on the pads. Yasir Ali works it away towards square leg. A single taken.
Kyle Jamieson drops this one short, outside off. Yasir Ali, on back foot, punches it towards deep cover for three runs.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Mehidy Hasan offers no shot on that.
Fullish delivery, around the off pole. Mehidy Hasan blocks it out.
Very full, around middle and leg. Driven to mid off.
Length, outside off. Mehidy Hasan defends this one towards point.
Back of a length delivery, outside off. Mehidy Hasan hangs back and defends this one off the back foot.
Fuller, on the pads. Yasir Ali clips it towards square leg for a single.
Good-length delivery, on middle and leg. Mehidy Hasan taps it to short leg.
FOUR! CUT AWAY! Tim Southee serves a shortish ball, outside off. Mehidy Hasan, on back foot, slashes this wide of gully for a boundary. 400 up for Bangladesh!
Length, on off. Mehidy Hasan blocks it out.
Shortish, outside off. Mehidy Hasan pushes it towards cover.
Angling it in from off, on a length. Mehidy Hasan blocks it out.
A full delivery, on the pads. Yasir Ali misses his flick and gets rapped on the pads.
Shorter this time, outside off. Yasir Ali leaves it alone.
Very full this time, around middle. Yasir Ali punches it past mid on for a single.
On a length, outside off. Mehidy Hasan offers no shot on that one.
Full delivery, outside off. Mehidy Hasan defends that solidly off the front foot.
Good length, wide outside off. Hasan leaves it alone. THAT WILL BE STUMPS ON DAY 3.
Rachin Ravindra starts off with a loopy ball, outside off. Yasir Ali leaves it alone.
Another flighted delivery, on middle. Yasir Ali prods and blocks it out.
Tosses it up again, around off. Yasir Ali lunges and defends it out.
Loopy delivery, outside off. Yasir Ali blocks it on the off side.
Very full, on middle. Yasir Ali pushes it to mid on.
Another flatter and fuller delivery. Yasir Ali eases it to mid on. Ravindra starts off with a maiden over!
Neil Wagner begins with a length delivery, outside off. Mehidy Hasan shoulders arms to it.
Touch fuller, outside off. Mehidy Hasan offers no shot on that.
Good-length delivery, around the fifth stump line. Mehidy Hasan lets that go through.
On a length, outside off. Left alone.
Good length, around off. Mehidy Hasan pushes it past point for a single.
Swing and a miss! A length delivery, outside off. Yasir Ali looks to cut that away but gets beaten on the extra bounce.
Loopy delivery, on middle. Mehidy Hasan lunges and blocks it out.

NOT OUT! Huge shout for LBW! Rachin Ravindra serves a loopy delivery, on middle. Mehidy Hasan gets down on his knee and looks too sweep this, and gets a slight edge onto the pad. A shout for LBW and the umpire raises his finger. The replay rolls in. UltraEdge confirms that Hasan has got some glove on it, and the decision needs to be overturned. Mehidy Hasan survives and New Zealand's hunt for a wicket continues.
Tosses it up, on middle. Blocked out.
Loopy ball, on middle. Hasan sweeps this and gets a top edge towards fine leg  for a brace.
Tuch shorter, outside off. Mehidy Hasan cuts that past point for a single.
Flatter, around off. Yasir Ali pushes it towards cover point. Dot to end the over.
Fuller in length, around off. Mehidy Hasan drives it to mid off.
Wagner drags his length back, around middle. Mehidy Hasan blocks it this time.

NOT OUT! Back of a length, around off. Mehidy Hasan stays back to block but he gets an inside edge onto his pad. Neil Wagner appeals and the umpire raises his finger. Hasan reviews it straightaway. The replays suggest that there was a big inside edge so the on-field decision is overturned! Hasan survives yet again!
Full ball, outside off. Mehidy Hasan squueezes it out to deep point for a run.
Back of a length, outside off. Yasir Ali blocks it off the back foot.
Length ball, around leg. Yasir Ali clips it to fine leg for a brace.
Tim Southee begins with a length ball, outside off, shaping it away. Yasir Ali leaves it alone.

FOUR! Nicely driven! Tim Southee serves it fuller in length, on off. Yasir Ali drives it past the diving fielder at mid off. The ball races away towards the boundary. First boundary of the day for Bangladesh.
Touch fuller again, on middle. Yasir Ali blocks it out.
Full and outside off, shaping it away. Yasir Ali leaves it alone.
Another outswinger, outside off, on a length. Yasir Ali offers no shot on that.
Good-length delivery, on middle. Yasir Ali, on back foot, blocks it.
Boult starts with a length ball, on middle. Mehidy Hasan blocks it out watchfully.

In the air..but safe! Banged into the deck, around leg. Mehidy Hasan swivels and pulls it uppishly behind square on the leg side. It falls just short of Kyle Jamieson at fine leg and the batters take a run.
Full ball, outside off. Yasir Ali prods and drives it past the mid off fielder. The batters take three runs.
Full ball, outside off. Mehidy Hasan leaves it alone.
BEATEN! Good-length ball, outside off and shaping away late. Mehidy Hasan lunges forward to defend but the ball goes past his outside edge.
Full ball, angling in from middle. Mehidy Hasan drives it towards mid on. Neil Wagner does well to cut it off and the batters take a single.
Full ball, outside off and curling away late. Mehidy Hasan looks to drive at first but decides to leave it in the end.
On a length, outside off. Mehidy Hasan leaves it alone.
Southee goes wider of the crease this time and hurls a full ball, outside off. Mehidy Hasan lets it be.
A wayward ball, angling down leg. Mehidy Hasan misses his flick.
NASTY! Southee bangs it into the deck, around middle. Mehidy Hasan looks to pull but he misses and gets hit just below his right shoulder. That will hurt and Hasan looks in pain.
Full ball, outside off. Mehidy Hasan drives it past the mid off fielder and the batters take three runs. Good running!
Back of a length, outside off. Mehidy Hasan sways away from the line of the ball.

FOUR! Nicely controlled by Hasan! Boult bangs it into the deck, around leg. Hasan stays back and pulls it along the ground behind square on the leg side for a bounday. This will surely frustrate Boult.
On a length, around off. Mehidy Hasan hangs back and blocks it to the off side.
Short of a length, on off. Mehidy Hasan defends it out.

Oh, dear! How did that miss the off stump? This is a peach of a delivery from Boult and Hasan is very lucky to get away with it! Length ball, just outside off and angling in late. Mehidy Hasan leaves it and the ball goes just past the off pole.
Back of a length, outside off. Mehidy Hasan does not offer any shot to this one.
Fuller in length, outside off. Yasir Ali leaves it alone.
Short of a length, outside off. Yasir Ali stays back and cuts it over the point fielder. The batters take a single.
Well bowled! Good-length ball, around off and shaping away late. Mehidy Hasan lets it be.
Another ball, on a length, just outside off and curling away late. Mehidy Hasan prods but decides to leave it in the end.
Southee bangs it into the deck, around middle. Mehidy Hasan ducks underneath.
Back of a length, around off. Mehidy Hasan defends it off the back foot.
Good-length delivery, shaping it onto the pads. Yasir Ali flicks it past square leg for a brace.
Change of angle now, Trent Boult goes 'round the wicket, serves a shortish delivery, outside off. Yasir Ali blocks it towards point.
Back of a length, on the body. Yasir Ali pulls it gently towards deep backward square leg for a single.
FOUR! Cleverly done! A length ball, onto the pads. Mehidy Hasan, on the back foot, just tickles it away towards the fine leg fence for a boundary. The lead is now past 100!
Nipping back in onto the pads, and on a length, Mehidy Hasan blocks it out on the leg side.
Touch shorter, outside off. Hasan pushes it to cover point.
Kyle Jamieson begins with a low full toss ball, around off. Yasir Ali pushes it back to the bowler.
Touch fuller, on the pads. Yasir Ali flicks it straight to mid-wicket.
Shortish delivery, outside off. Yasir Ali, on the back foot, pushes it wide of the short cover fielder, who dives and makes a good stop there.
Back of a length, outside off. Yasir Ali leaves it alone.
Fuller, down the leg side this time. Yasir Ali lets that go through.
Full, outside off. Yasir Ali offers no shot on that. Dot to end the over and a maiden over to start with!
Full in length, on middle. Mehidy Hasan, on front foot, drives it to the man at cover.
On a length, on middle. This time Mehidy Hasan hangs back and blocks it out.
Good length, outside off. Mehidy Hasan plays that to point.
Wide! Too short on this occasion. Mehidy Hasan just ducks under it. Wide called as the ball went way over Hasan's head.
FOUR! Top shot! A shortish delivery, outside off. Mehidy Hasan hangs back and pushes it through covers for a boundary.
LEG BYE! A fuller delivery, on the pads. Mehidy Hasan misses his flick and gets rapped on the pads. The ball rolls towards fine leg and the batters steal a leg bye.
Length ball, outside off. Yasir Ali pushes it to cover.

Good-length delivery, on the pads. Yasir Ali, on the back foot, tucks it to fine leg. The batters take two runs, but hang on, the umpire signals for a short run, as Ali is short of his crease as he turned for the second. One run given.
Length ball, shaping away from outside off. Left alone.
Another length ball, wide of off. Yasir Ali lets that go through.
Good length, outside off. Yasir Ali shoulders arms to it.

NEARLY CHOPPED ON! Back of a length, outside off. Yasir Ali, on the back foot, looks to cut this away, but manages to get a bottom edge. The ball bounces on the turf and goes just over the stumps. Yasir Ali gets lucky here.
Swinging it in this time, on middle. Yasir Ali blocks it out.
Length, on middle. Mehidy Hasan pushes it back to the bowler.
Another length ball, on the pads this time. Mehidy Hasan defends this one to mid-wicket.
Touch shorter, on the thigh pads. Mehidy Hasan tucks it away towards fine leg. A single taken.
Trent Boult goes over the wicket now, serves a length ball, outside off. Yasir Ali pushes it to cover.
Shortish ball, on the thigh pads again. Yasir Ali taps it past square leg for a single.
Shortish delivery, around off. Mehidy Hasan dabs it towards gully.
Length ball, jagging back in sharply, from off. Yasir Ali turns it to mid-wicket.
Lovely delivery! Good length ball, outside off and shaping away late. Yasir Ali looks to poke at it but the ball beats his outside edge.
On a length, outside off and shaping away late. Yasir Ali leaves it alone.
Jamieson goes a bit fuller this time, around middle. Yasir Ali defends it out.
Another full ball, around middle. Yasir Ali looks to block but it goes off the inner half of the blade towards square leg.
Length ball, angling in from middle. Yasir Ali prods and gets solid in his defense.
FOUR! EDGY! Back of a length, outside off. Mehidy Hasan sees the width and throws the kitchen sink at it. It goes off the thick outside edge and over the slip cordon for a boundary.
Length ball, around off. Mehidy Hasan blocks it out.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Tim Southee strikes and New Zealand get the much-needed breakthrough! A sigh of relief from Southee and Hasan's fighting knock comes to an end. This was a slightly shorter ball, outside off and shaping away late. Mehidy Hasan stays back and looks to cut but he only manages an outside edge towards the keeper. Tom Blundell behind the sticks makes no mistake and Bangladesh lose their seventh wicket now. Hasan walks back disappointed as he misses out on a well-deserved fifty.
Howout: c Tom Blundell b Tim Southee

Commentary: Full ball, angling down leg. Taskin Ahmed misses his flick.
A well-directed bumper from Southee, around middle. Taskin Ahmed ducks underneath.
Good-length ball, around middle. Taskin Ahmed blocks it out back to the bowler.
Length ball, angling in from middle. Yasir Ali tucks it to mid-wicket.
On a length, around off. Yasir Ali defends it off the front foot.
A wayward ball, down leg. Yasir Ali misses his flick.
Good-length ball, around off. Yasir Ali punches it to cover.
Wide! A bumper, well above Ali's head. Ali lets it go through to the keeper and the umpire stretches his arms to signal a wide.
On a length, outside off. Yasir Ali drives but finds the mid off fielder.
Back of a length, outside off. Yasir Ali gets behind the line of the ball to block this one out.
Full ball, angling in from middle. Taskin Ahmed clips it behind square on the leg side. The fielder at short fine leg does well to stop it by diving low to his right.
FOUR! A shot of some real authority from Ahmed! On a length, outside off. Ahmed stands tall, gets on top of the bounce and flat-bats it straight back past the bowler to fetch himself a boundary.
Good-length ball, around off. Taskin Ahmed blocks it out.
Back of a length, outside off. Taskin Ahmed stays back, opens the face of his bat and taps it towards the gully fielder.
Banged into the deck, around middle. Taskin Ahmed ducks underneath.
Full ball, drifting onto the pads. Taskin Ahmed flicks it uppishly but the ball falls just short of the mid-wicket fielder.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Oh, what an unfortunate way to get out and Yasir Ali would be absolutely gutted to get out in that manner! Jamieson serves a length ball, angling in down leg. Ali looks to flick but he gets a tickle on it. Tom Blundell, behind the sticks, does well to move across to his left and pouch it. Bangladesh lose another wicket and Jamieson is delighted!
Howout: c Tom Blundell b Kyle Jamieson

Commentary: Length ball, angling down leg. Shoriful Islam misses his flick.
Fuller and wider, outside off. Shoriful Islam looks to dig it out but he misses.
On a length, around off. Shoriful Islam blocks it out.
FOUR! Crucial runs these for Bangladesh! Full ball, outside off. Shoriful Islam throws his bat at it and the ball goes past the mid off fielder for a boundary.
Short ball, down leg. Shoriful Islam ducks udnerneath watchfully.
A length ball, angling in on middle. Taskin Ahmed looks to defend but gets an inside edge towards fine leg for a single.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Shoriful Islam drives it to cover.

Shoriful Islam takes the aerial route this time! Tim Southee serves a full ball, outside off. Shoriful Islam makes room and lofts over covers. The ball won't go all the way but the batters take two comfortable runs.
Another full delivery, outside off. Shoriful Islam drives it towards deep cover. A single taken.
Length, outside off. Taskin Ahmed blocks it out.

OUT! LBW! Tim Southee strikes again and sends Taskin Ahmed back to the hut. A length ball, angling it in onto the pads. Taskin Ahmed misses his flick and gets rapped on the pads. A huge shout for LBW and the umpire raises his finger. Taskin Ahmed reviews it straightaway. The replays roll in. UltraEdge confirms that there is no bat involved. Ball Tracker indicates that it would have clipped the leg stump. It is umpire's call and Bangladesh do not lose a review here, but lose a wicket.
Howout: lbw b Tim Southee

Commentary: Short ball, outside off. Shoriful Islam makes room and throw his arms at it, but fails to get any bat on it.

OUT! CLEANED HIM UP! Trent Boult wraps things up finally for New Zealand! Boult keeps it simple, serves a full ball, onto the stumps. Shoriful Islam backs away, exposes his stumps, goes for the drive but gets beaten altogether. The ball beats the edge and knocks the off stump over. BANGLADESH END ON 458 and THEY LEAD BY 130 RUNS.
Howout: b Trent Boult

Commentary: NOT OUT! A huge appeal straightaway! Taskin Ahmed serves a length ball, nipping back in sharply on middle. Tom Latham was thinking to leave that but gets his bat down late and gets rapped on the pads. A huge shout for LBW but the umpire is unmoved. Bangladesh do not go for the review.
Fuller, on the pads. Tom Latham tucks it away towards mid-wicket.
Too full this time, around off. Tom Latham drives it past mid off. Three runs taken.
Touch fuller again around off. Will Young blocks it solidly.
Fuller again, wide of off. Will Young leaves it alone.
A length ball, nipping back in on middle. Will Young shoulder arms to it. The ball goes over the stumps. Well left by Will Young!
Touch fuller, outside off. Tom Latham leaves it alone.

FOUR! First boundary for New Zealand! Edgy runs here! Shoriful Islam serves a short ball, outside off. Tom Latham stretches his arm and goes for the cut but gets a thick outside edge past gully for a boundary.
Good length, outside off. Tom Latham pushes it to cover.
Back of a length, outside off. Tom Latham hangs back and punches it through covers for three runs.
Full, on middle. Will Young nudges it towards mid-wicket.
Fuller again, around off. Blocked out.
Mehidy Hasan starts off with a loopy delivery, around middle. Tom Latham lunges and blocks it out.
Slower through the air, on middle. Tom Latham leans and defends it out.
Very full, slower again, around middle. Blocked out
Touch shorter, on middle. Tom Latham defends it out.
Much quicker this time, the ball skids through the deck here. Tom Latham does well to hang back and block it out.
Fuller, outside off. Tom Latham pushes it towards cover. THAT WILL BE LUNCH ON DAY 4!
Good-length delivery, on middle. Will Young blocks this one out on the leg side.
Extra bounce! A length ball, on middle. Will Young blocks it out and takes away the bottom hand to reduce impact.
Touch fuller, on middle. Will Young defends this one out.
Good-length ball, on the pads. Will Young tucks it away to fine leg. A single taken.
Length ball, outside off, swinging it away. Tom Latham leaves it alone.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Tom Latham blocks it out solidly.
Taskin Ahmed shapes this one back in outside off, on a length. Will Young leaves it alone.

Good-length ball, outside off. Will Young hangs back and pushes it towards cover. He scampers through to the other end. A slight fumble by Mominul Haque allows the batters to complete the run comfortably.
Length ball, darting it on the pads this time. Tom Latham misses his flick and gets hit on the thigh pads.
Touch shorter, outside off. Tom Latham lets that go through.
Shorter, around off. Tom Latham looks to play at it initially but bails out at the end.
Length ball, outside off. Tom Latham offers no shot on that.

BEATEN! That is a lovely delivery! A half-hearted appeal but the umpire says no. Good-length ball, around off and shaping away late. Will Young hangs back and looks to poke at it but the ball zips past his blade.
On a length, around off. Will Young blocks it out.
FOUR! Nicely done! Good-length ball, on off. Will Young lunges forward and just eases it through the vacant mid off region for a boundary. Sublime timing!
On a length, well outside off. Will Young leaves it alone.
Leg Bye! Back of a length, around leg. Will Young misses his flick and gets hit on his thigh pad. The ball rolls away towards fine leg for a leg bye.
Islam bowls it fuller this time, way outside off. Tom Latham lets it through to the keeper.
Good-length ball, outside off. Will Young leaves it alone for the keeper to collect.
Back of a length, around off. Will Young hangs back and blocks it out solidly.
Short of a length, outside off. Will Young stays back and punches it to cover.

FOUR! Easy pickings and once again the timing is sublime! This is a full ball, drifting onto the pads. Young clears his front leg and flicks it past the mid on fielder. The fielder gives it a chase but the ball wins in the end.
Good-length ball, outside off. Will Young defends it out.
Short of a length, around middle. Will Young stands tall and tucks it to mid-wicket.
Length ball, around off. Tom Latham prods and blocks it solidly.
Back of length, around middle. Latham gets solid in his defense yet again.
On a length, way outside off. Tom Latham leaves it alone.
A bit fuller this time, around off. Tom Latham defends it out watchfully.
This is on a length, around off. Tom Latham hangs back and defends.
FOUR! That is a lovely shot to end the over! A bit fuller in length, outside off. Tom Latham presses forward and caresses it past the mid off fielder for a boundary. He made it look so easy!

NO BALL! Length ball, angling in from middle. Young stays back and nudges it through the square leg region. Mushfiqur Rahim runs across to his left from fine leg, puts in a foot to stop the ball and the batters collect three runs. Taskin Ahmed oversteps and it is called as a no ball.
On a length, outside off. Tom Latham lets it be.
Full ball, way outside off. Tom Latham does not offer any shot to this one.
Full ball, outside off. Tom Latham prods and square drives it towards backward point. The fielder there does well to stop it.

OUT! CHOPPED ON! Huge wicket this for Bangladesh as New Zealand's skipper walks back to the hut! This is a back-of-a-length delivery, outside off. Latham hangs back and looks to block it but he only manages a thick inside edge which cannons onto his stumps. Taskin Ahmed is delighted as he gets his man! Disappointment for Latham and joy for the tourists! Top start for Bangladesh.
Howout: b Taskin Ahmed

Commentary: On a length, around off. Devon Conway presses forward to block this one out.
Length ball, well outside off. Devon Conway leaves it alone.
Length ball, angling in from off. Will Young defends it out.
On a length, around leg. Will Young tucks it to mid-wicket for a single.
Good-length ball, around off. Devon Conway keeps it out.
A bit fuller this time, around middle. Devon Conway works it to the leg side.
That one bounced quite sharply! On a length, around off and bouncing off from a length. Devon Conway looks to block but he gets hit high on his bat due to the extra bounce.
Full ball, on off. Devon Conway leans forward and pushes it to mid off.
Back of a length, outside off. Will Young, on back foot, blocks it towards cover.
Touch fuller, around off. Will Young leans and defends it solidly.
On a length, outside off. Will Young shoulders arms to it.
Fuller, on the pads. Will Young misses his flick and gets rapped on the pads. Half an appeal by Bangladesh and the umpire is unmoved.
Good-length delivery, around middle. Will Young tucks it to the fielder at mid-wicket.
Tad fuller, around off. Will Young prods and blocks it out. A maiden for Taskin Ahmed.
Shoriful Islam goes over the wicket, serves a full ball, around off. Devon Conway defends it out watchfully.
Length ball, outside off. Devon Conway blocks it out solidly.
Good-length delivery, around middle. Devon Conway works it away wide of mid on and scampers through to the other end.
Shoriful Islam drops it short this time, around middle. Will Young pulls it to deep square leg. A single taken.
Length ball, on the thigh pads. Devon Conway taps it towards fine leg. A single taken.

Huge shout for LBW, but turned down by the umpire. Shoriful Islam goes 'round the wicket, serves a back-of-a-length ball, nipping back in on the pads. Will Young goes for the pull but gets beaten and gets rapped on the thigh pad. Bangladesh appeal, but the umpire says no. Too high probably.
Ebadot Hossain starts off with a full delivery, wide of off. Devon Conway leaves it alone.
Pulling his length bak here, a length ball, outside off. Devon Conway pokes at it but gets an inside edge towards fine leg. A single taken.
Fuller, on the pads. Will Young flicks it to mid-wicket and runs across to the other end.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Devon Conway lets that go though.
Fuller, around off. Devon Conway, on the front foot, blocks it out.
Full in length, on the pads this time. Devon Conway flicks it to short mid-wicket.
Fuller in length, outside off. Will Young prods and blocks it.
In the air...but safe! A full delivery, outside off. Will Young pushes it uppishly just wide of extra cover. A single taken.
Full in length, angling in across off stump. Devon Conway blocks it out.
A length ball, outside off. Devon Conway leans and defends that.
A fuller ball, around middle. Devon Conway pushes it through the inner half of his bat towards mid on.
Short of a length, around off. Devon Conway looks to defend but gets an outside edge towards gully.
Full in length, around middle and leg. Will Young flicks it to short mid-wicket.
Ebadot Hossain gets some extra bounce from the short of length delivery. Will Young tires to tuck it away but misses and gets hit on the thigh pad.
Fuller, outside off. Will Young defends it towards point.
Length ball, around off. Will Young blocks it out.
Another good-length delivery, outside off. Will Young defends it watchfully.
FOUR! Edgy boundary! A length ball, around off. Will Young tries to defend that but gets a thick outside edge which flies in between slip and gully. The ball races away for a boundary.
Flatter ball, around off. Devon Conway blocks it off the front foot.
Flatter ball, around off. Devon Conway prods and keeps it out.
A bit quicker this time, around middle. Devon Conway blocks it watchfully.
A bit quciker this time, on a length, around middle. Devon Conway skips down and looks to block but he misses and gets rapped on the pads.
Fuller in length, outside off. Devon Conway shimmies down but blocks it in the end.
Fuller in length, just outside off. Devon Conway comes forward and keeps it out.
Good-length ball, around off. Will Young stays back and blocks.

NOT OUT! Will Young survives! Length ball, angling down leg. Young looks to flick but he misses and the ball goes to the keeper. Bangladesh appeal for a caught behind but the umpire is not interested! Mominul Haque opts for a review but the the UltraEdge suggests that there wasn't any bat involved and so Bangladesh lose a review.
Back of a length, on off. Will Young blocks it out.
On a length, around off. Will Young defends it solidly.
Length ball, around off. Will Young looks to block but it goes off the inner half of the blade to the leg side.
Back of a length, outside off. Will Young blocks it out.
Flatter ball, drifting onto the pads. Devon Conway keeps it out.
Flatter and quicker, around leg. Devon Conway looks to defend but he misses and gets hit on his pad. The ball rolls to the leg side for a leg bye.
Tossed up, on off. Will Young blocks it out.
Fuller in length, around off. Will Young lunges forward and keeps it out.
Overpitched ball, outside off. Will Young opens the face of his bat and works it past the backward point fielder for a couple of runs.
Loopy ball, on a length, around leg. Will Young tucks it to mid-wicket.
Full ball, outside off. Devon Conway looks to drive but it goes off the outer half of his blade past the diving point fielder for a couple of runs.
Length ball, outside off. Devon Conway drives it to the cover fielder.
On a length, well outside off. Devon Conway presses forward and works it to the cover fielder.
Length ball, nipping back in sharply, from middle. Devon Conway flicks it to mid-wicket.
FOUR! EDGY! Back of a length, just outside off. Devon Conway looks to drive on the up but it goes off the thick outside edge past the gully fielder for a boundary.
On a length, outside off. Devon Conway blocks it out solidly.
Tossed up, on a length, outside off. Will Young prods and turns it towards mid on.
This is fuller and wider, outside off. Will Young drives it straight to the mid off fielder.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Will Young lunges forward to block this one out.
Slightly shorter in length, around middle. Will Young hangs back and keeps it out.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Will Young gets behind the line of the ball to block it.
Overpitched ball, on off. Will Young digs it out back to the bowler. Just 1 run off the over!
Good-length ball, down the leg side. Will Young watches it sail through to the keeper.
Touch fuller this time, around off. Will Young blocks it towards point.
Fuller length again, darting it on the pads this time. Will Young flicks it past the mid-wicket fielder for a brace.
Full again, around middle and leg. Will Young tucks it to the fielder at mid-wicket.
Good-length delivery, around middle. Will Young pushes it to the man at square leg.
Touch fuller, around middle. Will Young blocks it out.
Tossing it up, around middle. Devon Conway lunges and defends it out.
Loopy delivery again, full and on middle. Devon Conway gets down on his knee and sweeps it towards fine leg for a single.
Flighted delivery, outside off. Blocked out.
Very full, around off. Will Young tucks it towards mid on for a single.
Quicker this time, shorter, around off. Devon Conway hangs back and defends it out.
Loopy delivery, around middle and leg. Devon Conway leans and blocks it out solidly.
Good-length delivery, shaping back in on middle. Will Young defends this watchfully.
Length delivery, on the pads this time. Will Young taps it to mid-wicket.
Fuller, around middle, at 140.4 clicks. Will Young defends it out.
Length delivery, around middle and leg, at 140.2 clicks. Will Young flicks it to square leg.
Fuller, on middle. Will Young pushes it towards mid on.
FOUR! Edged and four! A length delivery, outside off, shaping away a tad. Will Young drives and gets a thick outside edge, just wide of gully. The ball races away to the fence for a boundary.
A loopy ball, around middle. Devon Conway sweeps it towards square leg for a single.
Slower through the air, around off. Will Young leans and blocks it out.
Tosses it up, around off. Will Young prods and blocks it.

TWO BYES! What a peach of a delivery by Mehidy Hasan! A perfect off spinner! Mehidy Hasan serves a loopy one, full around middle. Will Young leans forward and gets beaten as the ball turns into him. The ball misses the stumps and Liton Das fails to collect that one. Two byes taken.
Tossing it up, around off. Will Young blocks it out.
Touch shorter, turning it in. Will Young defends it solidly.
Full ball, outside off. Devon Conway drives it past the cover fielder and takes a couple of runs.

OUT! TAKEN! Good review from Bangladesh and they get the much-needed breakthrough! This was a good-length ball, around off and nipping back in late. Devon Conway looks to tuck it to the leg side but it goes off the inside edge, ricochets off his pads and loops up in the air towards the gully region where Shadman Islam dives in front and takes a good catch. Bangladesh appeal but the umpire says no. The replays suggest that there was a faint tickle on it before the ball hit the pad and Devon Conway has to walk back to the hut. A successful review for the tourists!
Howout: c Shadman Islam b Ebadot Hossain

Commentary: A full ball, outside off. Ross Taylor blocks it out.
A full length again, outside off. Ross Taylor pushes it to mid off.
A huge shout for caught behind but turned down! A length ball, down the leg side. Ross Taylor misses his flick and the ball brushes off his thigh pad to the keeper.
Fuller, around off. Blocked out.
Touch shorter, around off. Will Young blocks it out off the back foot.
Slower through the air, wide of off. Will Young defends it out.

DROPPED! Will Young gets lucky once again! A shorter delivery, outside off. Will Young hangs back and looks to chop this but gets an outside edge back to the keeper. Liton Das behind the stumps fails to grab that and Will Young survives.
Tossing it up, outside off. Will Young leaves it alone.
Flighted delivery, around middle. Will Young leans forwards and defends it out.
Another tossed up delivery, around middle. Will Young sweeps it towards square leg for a single.
Back of a length, on off. Will Young blocks it to the off side.
Short of a length, outside off. Will Young sways away from the line of the ball.
Back of a length, outside off. Will Young does not offer any shot to this one.
On a length, around off. Will Young gets behind the line of the ball to block it out.
Well bowled! Good-length ball, just outside off and jagging back in late. Will Young looks to poke at it at first but decides to leave it in the end.
On a length, outside off. Will Young lets it be.
Tossed up, around off. Ross Taylor blocks it out back to the bowler.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Ross Taylor looks to cut but he misses and gets hit on his pad.
Fuller in length, outside off. Ross Taylor prods and paddles it towards fine leg for a single.
Flatter ball, turning in sharply. Will Young turns it to mid-wicket.
Sharp turn there! Flatter and quicker, on a length and spinning in sharply. Will Young stays back to flick but he misses and gets hit on the inside half of his pad.
Tossed up, outside off. Will Young covers his stumps and lets it through to the keeper.
NASTY! Back of a length, around off. Ross Taylor gets into a awkward tangle as he tries to block, it goes off his gloves towards the off side.

NOT OUT! Bangladesh have wasted their review here as it looked not out in real time as well. This is a length ball, angling down leg. Ross Taylor shuffles across and looks to flick but he misses. The ball just brushes his thigh pad before going to the keeper. Bangladesh appeal and the umpire says no. Ebadot Hossain convinces his skipper to opt for a review and Mominul Haque obliges! However, the replays roll in and it clearly suggests that the ball had clipped the thigh pad and not the bat.
Length ball, angling in from middle. Ross Taylor turns it to mid-wicket.
Fuller in length, outside off. Ross Taylor presses forward and carves it past the cover fielder. The fielder there gives it a chase and the batters take three runs.
Back of a length, outside off. Will Young leaves it alone.
Full ball, around off. Will Young blocks it solidly this time. THAT WILL BE TEA ON DAY 4!
Tossed up, on a length, outside off. Ross Taylor eases it to long on for a single.
Loopy ball, outside off. Will Young prods and pushes it to cover for a run.

An appeal for LBW as well as caught behind but the umpire says no! Tossed up, on a length, outside off and spinning in sharply. Ross Taylor presses forward and looks to nudge it to the leg side but he misses. The ball ricochets off his pad and goes to the first slip fielder who grabs it cleanly. That was spinning way down leg though and there wasn't any bat involved either.
Tossed up, around off. Ross Taylor blocks it off the front foot.
A bit shorter this time, around middle. Ross Taylor keeps it out.
Nicely tossed up, outside off. Ross Taylor lunges forward and clips it to mid-wicket.
Length ball, around the off pole. Will Young, off the back foot, defends it out.
Very full, on off. Will Young pushes it back to the bowler.
Back of a length, outside off. Will Young stands tall and punches past the point fielder. Three runs taken.
Fuller in length, around middle. Ross Taylor pushes it to mid on for a quick single.
Full again, on middle. Will Young defends that towards short mid-wicket.
Full in length, around off. Will Young blocks it back to the bowler.
Loopy ball, very full, on middle. Ross Taylor works it away to the fielder at short mid-wicket.
Tossed up, outside off. Ross Taylor lunges and drives it towards deep point for a brace.
Full, around middle and off. Ross Taylor blocks it watchfully.
Touch shorter, turning back in on middle. Ross Taylor defends it off the back foot.
Mehidy Hasan turns it in again on middle. Ross Taylor, on back foot, blocks it out.
Tosses this one up, full and on middle. Ross Taylor pushes it to mid on.
Back of a length, outside off. Will Young leaves that one alone.
Good-length delivery, an inswinger, outside off. Will Young offers no shot on that.
Taskin Ahmed drops it short this time, around off. Will Young pulls it towards square leg for a single.
Wide! Too short on this occasion, down the leg side. Ross Taylor lets that go. A wide called as the ball bounces over Ross Taylor's head.
On a length, around middle. Ross Taylor tucks it towards square leg for a single.
Good-length delivery, outside off, at 137.6 clicks. Will Young leaves it alone.
Length delivery, around the off pole. Will Young defends it out.
Tossed up, full and on middle. Ross Taylor prods and blocks it solidly.
Another loopy delivery, full and around middle and off. Ross defends it off the front foot.
Full delivery, darting it onto the pads this time. Ross Taylor flicks it past the short leg fielder for a single.
Loopy ball, around off. Will Young gets down and goes for the sweep but misses. The ball brushes off the batter's arm, body and then the helmet. It lands safely on the leg side.
Quicker this time, around middle. Will Young works it away towards square leg for a single.
Full delivery, around middle and off. Ross Taylor sweeps it uppishly past the short leg fielder. A single to end the over.
Fuller in length, outside the off stump. Ross Taylor miscues his drive towards cover.
Full in length, on middle. Ross Taylor pushes it back to the bowler. Taskin Ahmed uses his right foot to stop the ball.
Taskin Ahmed drops it short this time, around middle. Ross Taylor ducks underneath it.
Back of a length, outside off. Ross Taylor punches it to the fielder at cover.
A length ball, nipping back in on middle. Ross Taylor looks to flick but gets an inside edge onto his pads.
Full-length ball, outside the off stump. Ross Taylor drives it gently towards cover and scampers through to the other end. A single to end the over.
Uppish but safe! Tossed up, around middle and spinning in late. Ross Taylor gets down on his knee and looks to sweep but it goes off the toe end just past the mid-wicket fielder for a run.
Flatter ball, outside off. Will Young blocks it off the back foot.
Loopy ball, outside off. Will Young lunges forward and pushes it through covers for a run.
Flatter ball, around leg. Ross Taylor prods and pushes it to the leg side for a single.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Will Young gets back in his crease and defends it out.
Leg bye! Tossed up, outside off. Will Young gets down on his knee and looks to sweep but he misses and gets hit on his pad. The ball rolls to the off side for a leg bye.

Leg bye! An appeal for LBW but the umpire is unmoved! Length ball, nipping back in late from middle. Will Young misses his flick and gets hit low on his pad. The ball rolls away to the leg side and the batters sneak in another leg bye.
Full ball, outside off. Ross Taylor pushes it back to the bowler.
On a length, around middle. Ross Taylor flicks it past the diving mid-wicket fielder and collects a single.
Banged into the deck, outside off. Will Young stays back, swivels and pulls it along the ground towards deep square leg for a run.

NOT OUT! Another waste of a review from Bangladesh and they have been very poor with DRS today! This was a full ball, around off. Taylor hangs back and digs it out watchfully. Bangladesh appeal and they think that it hit the the pad first, The umpire says no and they opt for a review. The replays roll in and it indicates that it came off the bat and the ball was nowhere near the pad. Bangladesh have lost all of their reviews now!
Full ball, outside off. Ross Taylor drives it to mid off.

Falls just short of the slip fielder! Flatter ball, on a length, outside off. Will Young looks to defend off the back foot but he gets an outside edge which goes towards the first slip. The fielder there dives in front but the ball falls just ahead of him.
Fuller in length, on middle. Will Young blocks it out.
Flatter and quicker, around middle. Will Young looks to defend but it goes off the inner half of the blade towards square leg for a run.
Tossed up, fuller in length, outside off. Ross Taylor looks to sweep but he misses.
Play and a miss! Another full ball, outside off and turning in late. Ross Taylor goes for a wild swing through mid-wicket but fails to get any bat on it.
Flatter ball, down leg. Ross Taylor glances it towards fine leg and collects a run.
Islam starts with a length ball, around off. Ross Taylor blocks it out.
Islam strays on the pads. Ross Taylor clips it towards deep square leg for a single.
Good-length delivery, around off. Will Young gets behind the line of the ball to block it.
Short of a length, outside off. Will Young hangs back and taps it to backward point.
Shorter in length, outside off. Will Young stays back and opens the face of his bat to guide it towards the gully region.
Back of a length, well outside off. Will Young stays back and dabs it towards the slip cordon.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Taylor prods and keeps it out.
Loopy ball, on a length, outside off and turning in late. Ross Taylor defends it off the front foot.
Slower through the air, on a length, outside off. Ross Taylor blocks this one out.
Flatter ball, on a length, outside off and turning in sharply. Ross Taylor works it on the on side by smothering the spin nicely.
Flatter and quicker, around middle. Ross Taylor dabs it onto the turf.
Floated, fuller in length, outside off. Ross Taylor gets forward and defends this one solidly. A probing over from Mehidy Hasan and also his third maiden over of the innings!
BEATEN! A length ball, outside off. Will Young tries to defend that but gets beaten past the outside edge.
Good-length delivery, outside the off stump. Will Young blocks it towards cover.
Fuller, around off. Will Young leans and defends it towards point.
Length ball, outside the off pole. Will Young lets it pass at the end minute.
Length ball, around middle. Young tucks it to the fielder at short mid-wicket.
Good length, on middle. Will Young blocks it watchfully.

Slower through the air, outside off. Ross Taylor goes for the sweep but misses and gets rapped on the thigh pad. A shout for LBW, the umpire is unmoved. No reviews left here for Bangladesh, they cannot go upstairs.

DROPPED! Bangladesh's fielding has not been the best! Another chance goes down. A loopy ball, around middle. Ross Taylor goes for the slog-sweep and hits it to the fielder at deep mid-wicket. Shadman Islam there moves to his left a tad, gets down to take an easy catch but makes a complete mess of it. The batters take a single.
Loopy ball, very full, outside off. Will Young misses his sweep.
Touch shorter, outside off. Will Young guides it past the slip fielder for a brace.
Tossed up, outside off. Will Young prods and blocks it out.
Full, outside the off pole. Will Young pushes it through covers for a single.
Good-length ball, outside off. Will Young looks to block but it goes off the outside edge towards the first slip fielder, on the bounce. Good bowling from Islam!
On a length, outside off. Will Young blocks it to the off side.
Back of a length, way outside off. Will Young taps it to backward point.
Width on offer but Young fails to find the gap! Full ball, outside off. Young frees his arms and plays a square drive but straight to the man at backward point.
FOUR! Finds the gap this time and times it beautifully! Length ball, outside off. Will Young lunges forward and caresses it through the cover region to fetch himself a boundary.
Length ball, outside off. Will Young leaves it alone.
Loopy delivery, very full, on middle. Will Young drags it towards long on for a single.

Loopy delivery, full, outside off. Will Young blocks it and gets an outside edge towards third man for brace. FIFTY for Will Young! What a find he has been for the Kiwis! However, the job is only half done and Young would be well aware of that fact.
Touch short, turning in sharply. Will Young swings hard and misses and gets hit high on the pad.
Fuller, around middle. Will Young works it away past short leg.
Tad shorter, around off. Will Young, on the back foot, pushes it back to the bowler.
Loopy ball, outside off. Will Young lunges and blocks it out.
Swing and a miss! A length ball, outside off. Ross Taylor hangs back and looks to drive that but gets beaten.
BEATEN! Another one goes past the outside edge. A good-length ball, outside off. Ross Taylor looks to defend that but gets beaten as the ball zips past through the outside edge.

And again! Ross Taylor has a go at it again and misses. This one was a touch fuller, wide of off, forcing Ross Taylor to drive. Ross Taylor does go for the drive but gets beaten as the ball moves away from him.
Fuller, around middle. Ross Taylor pushes it towards mid on.

FOUR! Beautiful shot! Shoriful Islam serves a length ball, wide of off. Ross Taylor has been beaten thrice this over but still, nothing stops him. He uses the width, hangs back and chops that past point for a boundary.
Good-length ball, outside off. Ross Taylor blocks it watchfully.
FOUR! Nicely done! Tossed up, outside off. Will Young gets down on his knee and sweeps it behind square on the leg side for a boundary.
Flatter ball, around off. Will Young blocks it out.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Will Young defends it off the front foot.
A bit quicker this time, around off and turning in sharply. Will Young blocks it.
Flatter ball, spinning down leg. Will Young tucks it to the leg side.
Shorter in length, outside off. Will Young pounces on it and cuts it through the cover region. The batters take three runs and it also brings up the 50-run partnership between Young and Taylor!
Flatter ball, outside off. Will Young punches it through covers and collects a single.
Full ball, outside off. Ross Taylor defends it out.
On a length, outside off. Ross Taylor eases it to long off for a single.
This is a full ball, way outside off. Will Young prods and does not offer any shot to this one.
Flatter ball, coming on with the angle, from off. Will Young blocks it.
A quicker ball, shorter in length, around middle. Young rocks back and defends it out.
Length ball, on middle. Ross Taylor drives it to mid on.
Back of a length, jagging back in from middle. Ross Taylor misses his flick and gets hit high on his pad. Bangladesh appeal but the umpire is unmoved.
Good-length ball, on middle. Ross Taylor defends it out.
FOUR! UP AND OVER! Enough is enough, says Ross Taylor! Back of a length, outside off. Taylor stands tall and chips it over the bowler's head for a boundary.
Full ball, angling in from off. Ross Taylor blocks it from the crease. Some words being exchanged between Ebadot Hossain and Ross Taylor! Seems to be a friendly banter though!
Full ball, around middle. Ross Taylor drives it straight to the mid on fielder.
Flatter ball, turning down leg. Will Young nudges it to mid-wicket for a run.
Loopy ball, on middle. Ross Taylor works it to long on and takes a single.
Flatter and quicker, around leg. Will Young tucks it towards the short leg fielder.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Will Young stays back to cut but the ball goes past his blade.
Hasan fires in a quicker ball, on middle. Will Young works it to long on for a single.
Slower through the air, on a length, around middle. Taylor gets behind the line of the ball to block it.
Back of a length, around off. Will Young defends it off the back foot.

Oh, dear! Absolute chaos in the middle and Ross Taylor is lucky to still be out in the middle. Sloppy from Bangladesh and a run out chance goes begging now! This was a good-length ball, outside off. Will Young taps it to the gully fielder. Taylor wanted a single and he is halfway down the pitch. Young obliges at the start but bails out in the end. The fielder at gully throws the ball back to bowler who is away from the stumps. Ebadot Hossain collects the ball and whips it towards the stumps at his end but misses. Taylor runs towards the danger end and makes it in the end. Lucky escape for the veteran!
A length ball, nipping back in onto the pads. Will Young tucks it towards square leg.
Full delivery, outside off. Will Young guides it past gully. Two runs taken here.
Good-length ball, around middle. Will Young blocks it off the back foot.
Another length delivery, on the pads. Will Young glances it to fine leg for a single.
Fuller, turning it away. Will Young hangs back and pushes it back to the bowler.
Shorter, outside off. Will Young hangs back and cuts that through cover for a single.
Tossed up, on middle. Ross Taylor prods and defends it.
Another loopy delivery, on middle. Ross Taylor blocks it out solidly.
Touch short this time, outside off. Ross Taylor advances down the track and then hangs back and chops it towards point.
Full, on middle. Ross Taylor defends it off the front foot.
Swing and a miss! A length ball, shaping it away wide of off. Will Young waits back and looks to chop this, but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Fuller this time, on middle. Will Young taps it towards mid-wicket.
FOUR! Streaky! A length ball, wide off. Will Young hangs back and slices through the outer half of his bat towards third man for a four! And New Zealand are in the lead!
Ebadot Hossain drops it short this time, around middle. Will Young pulls it towards square leg for a single.
Short ball, outside off. Ross Taylor pulls it along the ground towards deep mid-wicket for a run.
Back of a length, outside off. Will Young hangs back and blocks it out.
Fuller, outside off. Ross Taylor, on the back foot, cuts it to the fielder at point. He leaves his crease for a run but is sent back by his partner.
Tosses it up, full and on middle. Ross Taylor blocks it towards mid-wicket.
Fuller again, outside off. Ross Taylor drives it towards cover for a single.
Quicker this time, around off. Will Young blocks it out off the back foot.
Loopy delivery, on middle. Will Young advances down the pitch and blocks it out.
Another full delivery, on off. This is driven back to the bowler.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Ross Taylor defends it out.
Full, on middle and off. Ross Taylor pushes it towards mid-wicket for a single.

OUT! CLEANED HIM UP! Ebadot Hossain strikes at last and has broken the partnership! Will Young makes his way back to the hut. A length delivery, around off. Will Young swings his bat at it as he tries to heave it to the leg side but fails to connect and the ball nips back in and knocks the bails over. Will Young walks back nodding his head, not the way he would have liked to go. But that's the end of a solid innings.
Howout: b Ebadot Hossain

Commentary: A loud shout for LBW but the umpire is unmoved! Length ball, angling in from middle. Henry Nicholls misses his flick and gets hit high on his pad.

OUT! BOWLED! Whoaaa! Ebadot Hossain is turning the game on its head and New Zealand lose two wickets in an over! Ebadot Hossain is on a roll! He serves a full ball which jags back sharply from off. Henry Nicholls stays back and looks to drive on the up but the ball sneaks through his bat and pad and crashes onto his stumps. Bangladeshi's are delighted and New Zealand are in a spot of bother now! Terrific passage of play for the tourists and they are well and truly ahead in this contest!
Howout: b Ebadot Hossain

Commentary: A length ball, angling back in outside off. Tom Blundell blocks it out. End of a wonderful over by Ebadot Hossain.
Slower through the air, around off. Ross Taylor leans and blocks it out.
Touch shorter, turning it onto the pads. Ross Taylor waits back and flicks it towards square leg.
Loopy ball, around middle. Ross Taylor stands deep in his crease and defends it with the toe-end of the bat.
Full, around middle. Ross Taylor blocks it solidly.
Tossing it up, around middle. Ross Taylor lunges and defends it watchfully.
Quicker this time, around middle. Ross Taylor pushes it towards mid-wicket.
BEATEN! A yorker-length delivery, outside off. Tom Blundell looks to drive this but gets beaten on the inside edge.
Angling in across off, on a good length. Tom Blundell blocks it out.

OUT! LBW! Ebadot Hossain bags another wicket! He has sent Tom Blundell back early. A length ball, nipping back in onto the pads. Tom Blundell hangs back, and misses his flick to get hit on the pads. A huge shout for LBW, this time the umpire raises his finger. Tom Blundell opts for a review. The replays roll in and the UltraEdge confirms that there is no bat involved in that. The Ball Tracker shows three reds, which means Tom Blundell needs to depart and Ebadot Hossain grabs his fourth wicket. New Zealand lose a review here and have lost their fifth wicket.
Howout: lbw b Ebadot Hossain

Commentary: Full ball, around off. Rachin Ravindra digs it out to the off side.
Hossain errs in line and spills this one down leg. Rachin Ravindra misses his flick.
Length ball, way outside off. Rachin Ravindra square-drives it towards backward point.
Tossed up, outside off. Ross Taylor drives it through the cover region for a single.
Flatter ball, on off. Rachin Ravindra prods and blocks it out.
Slightly shorter in length, outside off. Rachin Ravindra stays back and punches it to mid off.
Another ball, shorter in length, outside off. Rachin Ravindra blocks it out.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Rachin Ravindra defends it off the front foot.
FOUR! Cut away! Flatter and quicker, outside off. Rachin Ravindra rocks back and cuts it past the point fielder and bags a boundary.
Length ball, around off. Ross Taylor blocks it out.
A low full toss, around middle. Ross Taylor turns it wide of mid on and collects a single.
Full ball, outside off. Rachin Ravindra leaves it alone.
Shorter in length, around off. Rachin Ravindra blocks it out watchfully.
Length ball, jagging back in sharply from outside off. Rachin Ravindra leaves it alone and the ball goes just past his off pole.
Back of a length, around off. Rachin Ravindra keeps it out.
Flatter ball, on a length, around middle. Ross Taylor blocks it out towards short leg.
Flatter ball, around off and turning in late. Ross Taylor tucks it to the leg side.
Flatter and quicker, around middle. Rachin Ravindra nudges it to the leg side.
Fuller in length, outside off. Rachin Ravindra gets forward and defends it.
Flatter ball, coming in with the angle. Rachin Ravindra gets into a tangle but somehow manages to get his bat down in time.
Flatter ball, around off. Rachin Ravindra prods to block but it goes off the shoulder of his bat and falls just wide of the silly point fielder.

Oh, dear! Had that been a direct hit, Ross Taylor was a goner! Length ball, on middle. Ross Taylor tucks it to square leg and looks for a single. Rachin Ravindra says no. Shoriful Islam collects the ball from square leg and has a shy at the striker's end but he misses and Taylor survives!
A yorker-length ball, on off. Ross Taylor digs it out.
Full ball, around off. Ross Taylor keeps it out watchfully.
This is a length ball, angling down leg. Ross Taylor misses his flick and the keeper does well to move across to his left to gather the ball.
Full ball, way outside off. Ross Taylor shoulders his arms to this one.
Length ball, jagging back in from off. Ross Taylor gets forward and blocks it out. Top over from Ebadot Hossain! His fourth maiden of the innings.
Tossed up, on middle. Rachin Ravindra defends it out.
Flatter ball, around middle. Rachin Ravindra nudges it to the leg side for a run.
Slightly shorter in length, outside off. Ross Taylor punches it to deep cover for a single.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Rachin Ravindra drives it wide of mid off and takes a run.
Flatter ball, coming on with the angle from off. Ross Taylor defends it off the front foot.
Looped up, on a length, around off. Ross Taylor prods and blocks it out.
Flatter ball, around off. Rachin Ravindra is solid in his front foot defense.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Rachin Ravindra gets behind the line of the ball to block it.
On a length, outside off. Rachin Ravindra punches it to cover.
Looped up, around leg. Rachin Ravindra prods and does not offer any shot to it. The ball hits him on his pad.
Tossed up, around off. Rachin Ravindra presses forward to block it.
This is a bit quicker, on a length, around middle. Rachin Ravindra gets forward and defends it solidly.
Back of a length, around leg. Ross Taylor nudges it to the leg side and collects a single.
Short of a length, outside off. Rachin Ravindra stays back and punches it to cover.
Hossain comes 'round the wicket and serves a good-length ball, around off. Rachin Ravindra presses forward to block this one out.
Fuller in length, outside off. Rachin Ravindra gets forward and dabs it to the off side.
Fuller in length, around middle. Rachin Ravindra clips it towards Mominul Haque at mid-wicket who has a shy at the bowler's end but he misses.

Hossain changes his angle for the last ball, comes over the wicket and serves a good-length ball, just outside off which curls away late. Rachin Ravindra shoulders his arms to it. THAT WILL BE STUMPS ON DAY 4!
Length ball, nipping back in late from middle. Taylor glances it towards fine leg for a single. New Zealand are up and running on Day 5!
Full ball, way outside off. Rachin Ravindra leaves it alone.
On a length, around off. Rachin Ravindra blocks it off the front foot.
FOUR! Glorious! Taskin goes a bit fuller this time, outside off. Rachin Ravindra presses forward and carves it through the cover-point region for a boundary.
Taskin comes 'round the wicket and serves a length ball, outside off. Rachin Ravindra lets it through to the keeper.
Good-length ball, around off. Rachin Ravindra defends it out.
Hossain starts with a full ball, outside off. Ross Taylor prods and pushes it past the cover fielder and collects a couple of runs.

OUT! CHOPPED ON! Ebadot Hossain continues to impress and he bags a five-wicket haul! He is carrying on from where he left off on Day 4 and gets the big wicket of Ross Taylor. This was a length ball, angling in from off. Taylor looks to block with an angled bat and it goes off the inside edge onto the stumps. Just the kind of start that the tourists were hoping for and New Zealand are in deep trouble now and Taylor makes his way back to the pavilion.
Howout: b Ebadot Hossain

Commentary: Length ball, outside off. Kyle Jamieson leaves it alone.
Full ball, outside off. Kyle Jamieson defends it to the off side.
Back of a length, around off. Kyle Jamieson prods and blocks it back to the bowler.
Good-length ball, around the fourth stump channel. Kyle Jamieson looks to block but it goes off the inside edge onto the deck. Top over from Ebadot Hossain!
Length ball, around middle. Rachin Ravindra pushes it towards mid on.
Short of a length, around middle. Rachin Ravindra keeps it out watchfully.
On a length, way outside off. Rachin Ravindra lets it be.
Back of a length, jagging back in from outside off. Rachin Ravindra gets behind the line of the ball to block it.
Length ball, angling down leg. Rachin Ravindra clips it towards fine leg and collects a run.
Length ball, angling down leg and going on with the angle. Kyle Jamieson misses his flick.
Length ball, jagging back in from outside off. Rachin Ravindra prods to block but it goes off the outer half of the bat towards the gully region.
FOUR! EDGY! This was a good-length ball, angling in from outside off. Rachin Ravindra has a tentative poke at it and it goes off the outside edge past the diving keeper and into the third man fence.

A bit sloppy from Bangladesh now! Good-length ball, around leg. Rachin Ravindra tucks it towards square leg. The fielder there collects the ball and has a needless shy at the striker's end but misses. The batters steal a run.
Back of a length, outside off. Kyle Jamieson blocks it to the off side.
On a length, around off. Kyle Jamieson looks to block but it goes off the inside edge onto the deck.

OUT! TAKEN! That is a stunner from Shoriful Islam at mid-wicket and New Zealand lose another wicket! It is that man again, Ebadot Hossain gets his sixth wicket of the innings! This was a length ball, nipping back in from middle. Kyle Jamieson flicks it uppishly towards mid-wicket. Shoriful Islam there dives full stretch to his right and takes a blinder.
Howout: c Shoriful Islam b Ebadot Hossain

Commentary: Full ball, around off. Rachin Ravindra blocks it out.
Length ball, jagging back in from off. Rachin Ravindra defends it off the front foot.
A bit fuller in length, outside off. Rachin Ravindra pushes it towards mid off.
On a length, way outside off. Rachin Ravindra does not offer any shot to this one.
Well bowled! Short of a length, just outside off and curling away late. Rachin Ravindra looks to poke at it but leaves it in the end.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Taskin Ahmed joins the party now and New Zealand slip further. What a morning this is turning out to be for Bangladesh! Taskin hurls a full ball, outside off and inviting the batter to drive. Rachin Ravindra looks for a booming drive through the cover region but he only manages an outside edge and Liton Das behind the sticks does the rest. Taskin Ahmed is pumped and Bangladesh seem to be in a hurry to finish things off on Day 5!
Howout: c Liton Das b Taskin Ahmed

Commentary: LEG BYE! A length ball, on the thigh pad. Tim Southee misses his flick and the ball deflects off his thigh pad and rolls towards fine leg. The batters steal a leg bye.
Back of a length, around middle, nipping back in. Neil Wagner blocks it out.
Swing and a miss! Good-length ball, outside off. Neil Wagner swings hard at that one but fails to get any bat on it.
Fuller this time, on middle. Neil Wagner dabs it towards cover.
On a length, shaping back in on middle. Neil Wagner defends that one.
A length ball, outside off. Neil Wagner, on the back foot, pushes it to cover.

NOT OUT! A huge appeal for LBW but turned down! That did look close! A full delivery, shaping back in onto the pads. Tim Southee misses his flick and gets rapped on the pads. Bangladesh appeal for LBW but the umpire is unmoved. That was probably sliding down leg.
Nipping back in again, on middle. Tim Southee blocks it out.

OUT BOWLED! Another one bites the dust! Taskin Ahmed strikes again and sends back Tim Southee. An inswinging low full toss by Taskin Ahmed which comes back in sharply from outside off. Tim Southee goes for the drive but the ball sneaks through and cannons onto his stumps. New Zealand are now 9 down.
Howout: b Taskin Ahmed

Commentary: Another full toss, on the body. Trent Boult defends it out.

NOT OUT! Another shout for LBW, but the umpire says no! A full, inswinging ball. Trent Boult shuffles across and gets a slight edge onto his pads while going for his flick. Bangladesh appeal for LBW, but the umpire is unmoved.
NOT OUT! Another shout for LBW, but the umpire says no! Good-length ball, outside off and nipping back in. Trent Boult looks to block but gets an inside edge onto the pad.
Fuller, on the stumps. Neil Wagner pushes it back to the bowler.
Another full delivery, outside off. Neil Wagner drives it to cover fielder.
Low full toss this time. Neil Wagner pushes it towards mid on.
A length ball, outside off. Neil Wagner goes for the drive but gets beaten past the outside edge.
And again! Another length ball, outside off. Neil Wagner tries to block that but the ball zips past the outside edge.
Good-length ball, outside off. Left alone.
FOUR! Nicley done! A full delivery, around off. Trent Boult drives it uppishly past mid off. The ball races away to the fence for a boundary.
FOUR! Another boundary! Taskin Ahmed serves a length ball, wide of off. Trent Boult hangs back, and chops that aerially towards deep point for four.
Taskin Ahmed drops it short this time, around leg. Trent Boult ducks underneath.
Good-length delivery, on middle. Trent Boult blocks it out.
Fuller and wider of the off pole this time. Trent Boult swings hard at this but gets no bat on it.
A length ball, down the leg side. Trent Boult goes for the flick but misses. Bangladesh think that he has got some bat on it and they appeal for caught behind but the umpire is unmoved.
Good-length delivery, on off. Neil Wagner blocks it off the back foot.
Another length delivery, around the middle stump. Neil Wagner pushes it towards mid-wicket.
Length ball, outside off. Neil Wagner pushes it to cover.
Good-length delivery, around off. Neil Wagner looks to heave this but gets a thick inside edge on to his pads.
On a length, around the fifth stump. Neil Wagner punches it to cover off the back foot.
Angling in around off, on a length. Neil Wagner plays across the line and goes for the pull shot but gets an inside edge onto his pads.
Flatter ball, around off. Trent Boult skips down and blocks it out.
Tossed up, outside off. Trent Boult reaches out and blocks it towards point.
Fuller in length, outside off. Trent Boult defends it off the front foot.

OUT! TAKEN! Another terrific catch and Bangladesh have been top-notch in the field on Day 5! A loopy delivery, around off. Trent Boult advances down the track and goes for a big one. He plays across the line again and heaves it with the lower part of his bat. The ball flies towards deep mid-wicket. Taijul Islam (sub) there, runs to his left and times his leap perfectly to take a sensational catch to dismiss Trent Boult. New Zealand are bundled out for 169! BANGLADESH NEED 40 RUNS TO WIN!
Howout: c sub Taijul Islam b Mehidy Hasan

Commentary: Trent Boult begins with a length ball, outside off. Shadman Islam leaves it alone.
Touch fuller this time, wide of off. Shadman Islam cuts that away past point for a brace. Shadman Islam and Bangladesh are underway!
A length ball, nipping back in onto the pads. Shadman Islam plays it with soft hands and manages to get an outside edge towards point.
A length ball, shaping it away outside off. Shadman Islam shoulders arms to it.
Touch fuller, angling it onto the pads. Shadman Islam works it away towards fine leg. A single taken.
Back of a length, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto lets that go through.
Tim Southee begins with a length ball, swinging it in on middle. Shadman Islam blocks it out solidly.
Tad fuller, down the leg side this time. Shadman Islam tucks it to square leg.
Shortish delivery, around leg. Shadman Islam misses his flick and gets hit on the body.
Fuller, outside off. Shadman Islam blocks it solidly.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! New Zealand have their first breakthrough! Tim Southee strikes and sends Shadman Islam back in the hut early. Back of a length, outside off. Shadman Islam has a poke at it away from his body and manages to get an edge back to the keeper. Tom Blundell behind the stumps takes an easy catch. No celebrations for the Kiwis.
Howout: c Tom Blundell b Tim Southee

Commentary: Back of a length, around off. Mominul Haque blocks it towards cover.
Length ball, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto keeps it out.
On a length, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it towards cover.
Full ball, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto gets solid in his defense.
Back of a length, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto looks to cut but it goes off the inner half of the blade and onto the deck.

Length ball, angling in from middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto looks to defend but he misses and gets hit on his pad. Trent Boult appeals but the umpire says no. Tom Latham decides to review it but the Ball Tracker shows that the ball would have gone down leg and the on-field decision stays. New Zealand lose a review.
Good-length ball, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto lets it be.
Tim Southee drops it short, around off. Mominul Haque, on the back foot, pushes it to point.
A length ball, wide of off. Mominul Haque leans and leaves it alone.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Mominul Haque lets that go through to the keeper.
A length ball, angling it in on middle. Mominul Haque defends it out.
Fuller this time, on middle. Mominul Haque drives it to mid on.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Mominul Haque blocks it watchfully. A maiden over from Tim Southee.
Touch fuller, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto leaves it alone.
A length ball, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it out off the back foot.
Touch fuller again, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto tries to chop this but misses due to the lack of bounce. That one stayed really low.
Good-length ball, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto defends it out.
Another length delivery, on the stumps this time. Najmul Hossain Shanto hangs back and pushes it towards mid on.
Back of a length, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto, on back foot, blocks it towards point.
Banged into the deck, around middle. Mominul Haque ducks underneath.

FOUR! Streaky but Bangladesh won't mind that at all! A full ball, outside off. Mominul Haque reaches out and looks to drive but it goes off the thick outside edge past the gully fielder for a boundary.
BEATEN! Good-length ball, outside off. Mominul Haque looks to defend but the ball zips past his outside edge.
On a length, around off. Mominul Haque defends it out.
Back of a length, around off. Mominul Haque rides the bounce nicely and keeps it out.
A bit fuller this time, around off. Mominul Haque prods and blocks it solidly.
This is a length ball, angling in from middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it towards the leg side.
Banged into the deck, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto ducks underneath.
Good-length ball, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto stays back and blocks. That one stayed really low though!
Fuller in length, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto drives it but Neil Wagner does well at mid off to stop the ball.
Back of a length, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto hangs back and punches it past the point fielder for a single.
BEATEN! Top delivery from Boult! Good-length ball, around the corridor of uncertainty. Mominul Haque presses forward to block but the ball whistles past his blade.
On a length, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto defends it out.
Good-length ball, on middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto turns it to the leg side.
FOUR! EDGY! Full ball, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto looks for a booming drive but it goes off the outside half of the blade past the point fielder for a boundary.
Good-length ball, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it out.
FOUR! Top shot! Fuller in length, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto prods and caresses it past the cover fielder to fetch himself a boundary.
Good-length ball, on middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it solidly.
Back of a length, around off. Mominul Haque stays back and defends it nicely.
On a length, just outside off. Mominul Haque skips down and blocks it to the off side.
Fuller in length, outside off. Mominul Haque drives but the cover fielder dives and stops the ball.
A bumper, around middle. Mominul Haque ducks underneath.
Back of a length, outside off. Mominul Haque shoulders his arms to it.
Back of a length, around off. Mominul Haque gets behind the line of the ball and blocks it out.
Banged into the deck, around leg. Najmul Hossain Shanto ducks underneath watchfully.
Length ball, jagging back in from middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto looks to block but it goes off the inner half of the blade towards square leg for one.
Back of a length, outside off. Mominul Haque stays back and dabs it towards the gully fielder.
Full ball, angling in from outside off. Mominul Haque leaves it alone.

FOUR! Edged and a boundary! Full and wide, outside off. Mominul Haque sees the width and looks to drive but it goes off the outside half of the blade past the backward point fielder. The ball races away to the fence.
FOUR! AND AGAIN! Full ball, way outside off. Mominul Haque looks to drive yet again but it flies off the outside edge past the diving gully fielder and into the third man fence.
Full ball, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto drives it towards mid off.
Back of a length, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto stays back to block but gets an inside edge onto the deck.
Back of a length, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto hangs back and blocks it solidly.
Length ball, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto gets behind the line of the ball and defends it.
FOUR! EDGY! Short of a length, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto sees the width and throws his bat at it. It goes off the thick outside edge past the diving gully fielder for a boundary.
Fuller in length, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto drives it to mid off.
Wagner starts with a full ball, on middle. Mominul Haque pushes it to mid on.
Back of a length, on middle. Mominul Haque blocks it solidly.
Full ball, around off. Mominul Haque drives it back to the bowler. Neil Wagner gets his left hand to it and the ball ricochets off his hand and hits the stumps at the non-striker's end.
On a length, around off. Mominul Haque defends it solidly.
Short of a length, outside off. Mominul Haque is solid in his defense.
Back of a length, around off. Mominul Haque blocks it to the off side.
Full ball, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto drives it towards mid off.
Jamieson drags his length back and serves a good-length delivery, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it out.
Good-length ball, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto gets behind the line of the ball to block it.
Short of a length, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto defends it.
Good-length ball, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it out nicely.
Wide! A bumper, on middle and going way above the batter's head. Najmul Hossain Shanto ducks underneath and the umpire signals a wide for the height.
Back of a length, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto leaves it alone.
Full ball, outside off. Mominul Haque presses forward and drives it to cover.
Leg bye! Full ball, angling in from middle. Mominul Haque misses his flick and gets hit low on his pad. The ball rolls to the leg side for a leg bye.
Fuller in length, outside off. Mominul Haque just pushes it past the bowler and the batters take three runs. Trent Boult does well to save a run for his side.
Good-length ball, on off. Mominul Haque blocks it to the off side.
Length ball, angling in from middle. Mominul Haque turns it to mid-wicket.
Back of a length, nipping back in from off. Mominul Haque stays back and keeps it out.
Length ball, way outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto leaves it alone.

OUT! TAKEN! Too little, too late for the Kiwis but that is a terrific catch from the veteran, Ross Taylor! This was a length ball, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto has a poke at it and the ball goes off the outside edge towards the right of Taylor at first slip. Taylor reacts a bit late but moves to his right, gets low and takes a one-handed stunner!
Howout: c Ross Taylor b Kyle Jamieson

Commentary: An appeal for LBW but the umpire says no. Good-length ball, angling in from middle. Mushfiqur Rahim looks to flick but gets an inside edge onto his pad.
Full ball, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim digs it out to mid-wicket.
Back of a length, around off. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out.
Length ball, angling in from middle. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it off the front foot.
Good-length ball, outside off. Mominul Haque drives but straight to the cover fielder.
Full ball, on middle. Mominul Haque pushes it to mid on.
NO BALL! On a length, outside off. Mominul Haque prods and pushes it to mid off. Neil Wagner oversteps and the umpire signals a no ball.
Back of a length, outside off. Mominul Haque hangs back and dabs it to the slip fielder.
Short of a length, jagging back in from outside off. Mominul Haque lets it be.
Full ball, outside off. Mominul Haque looks to drive but it goes off the inner half of the blade to mid on.
Fuller in length, outside off. Mominul Haque drives it to the cover fielder.
Wide! Full and too wide, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone and the umpire stretches his arms to signal it as a wide.
Back of a length, around leg. Mushfiqur Rahim stays back to block but it goes off the inside edge towards fine leg for a single.
Full ball, outside off. Mominul Haque drives it towards mid off.
Short of a length, angling down leg. Mominul Haque nudges it behind square on the leg side for a single.
On a length, nipping back in from off. Mushfiqur Rahim stays back to block.

FOUR! There it is! Mushfiqur Rahim hits the winning runs and Bangladesh create history! Back of a length, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim hangs back and guides it past the point fielder to bag a boundary. Mushfiqur Rahim celebrates their win with a roar and fist pump. BANGLADESH WIN THE TEST BY 8 WICKETS!
